var book = {
	"name": "2 Khronikl",
	"numChapters": 36,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la pynkhlaiñ ïa u Solomon u khun u Dabid ha ka Hima jong u, bad U Trai U Blei jong u, U la don ryngkat bad u, bad U la pynkhraw ïa u shikatdei eh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Solomon u la kren ha ki Israel baroh, ha ki rangbah shihajar bad jong ki shispah, bad ha ki nongbishar, bad ha man la u nongïalam ha ki Israel baroh, kiba ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumta, u Solomon, bad baroh u paidlang lem bad u, ki la ïaleit sha ka jaka bajrong kaba la don ha Gibeon; naba hangta ka la don Ka Ïingjaiñ Ka Jingïaseng ka jong U Blei, ïa kaba u Moses u shakri jong U Trai u la thaw ha ka ri khlaw.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u Dabid u la lah wallam ïa ka synduk jong U Blei na Kiriath-jearim sha ka jaka kaba u Dabid u la pynkhreh ïa ka: naba u la pynïeng ka ïingjaiñ ïa ka ha Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ïa ka duwan rnong ruh, kaba la thaw u Besalil u khun u Uri, u khun u Hur, ka la don hangta ha khmat Ka Tabernakl jong U Trai: bad u Solomon bad u paidlang ki la ïawad sha ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Solomon u la leit kiew shata sha ka duwan rnong ha khmat U Trai, kaba la don ha ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng, bad u la ainguh shi hajar tylli ki jingainguh thang halor jong ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ha kata ka miet, U Blei u la paw ha u Solomon, bad u la ong ha u, “To pan ngan ai aïu ïa me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Solomon u la ong ha U Blei, “Me la leh ka jinglehsbun kaba khraw ha u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad me la pynlong syiem ïa nga ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te, A Trai uba U Blei, to ai ba ka jingkular jong me ha u Dabid u kpa jong nga kan long kaba la pynskhem: naba me la pynlong syiem ïa nga halor u paidlang uba kum ka 'dewmet ka khyndew ha ka jingbun paid.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> To ai ha nga mynta, ïa ka jingstad bad ïa ka jingtip, ba nga lah ban leit shabar bad wan shapoh ha khmat une u paidlang: namar uei uba lah ban bishar ïa une u paidlang jong me, uba bun katta katta?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Blei u la ong ha u Solomon, “Namar ba kane ka la don ha ka dohnud jong me, bad ba mem shym la pan ïa ka spah, ka jingdon, lane ïa ka burom, lymne ïa ka jingim jong kita kiba shun ïa me, lymne mem shym la pan ruh ïa ka ban im slem: hynrei, me la pan ïa ka jingstad bad ïa ka jingtip na ka bynta ïa lade hi, ba me lah ban bishar ïa u paidlang jong nga, halor uba nga la pynlong syiem ïa me:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ïa kata ka jingstad bad ka jingtip la ai ha me; bad ngan ai ha me ïa ka spah, bad ka jingdon, bad ka burom, kat kita ym don uno uno ruh na ki syiem kiba la long ha shuwa jong me uba la ïoh, lymne un ym don shuh uno uno ruh hadien jong me u ban ïoh ïa kiba kumjuh.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, u Solomon u la wan noh na la ka jingleit sha ka jaka bajrong kaba la don ha Gibeon, na khmat ka ïingjaiñ jong ka jingïaseng, sha Jerusalem; bad u la synshar halor ki Israel.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Solomon u la ïalum ïa ki kali bad ïa ki nongshong kulai: bad u la don shi hajar sawspah ki kali, bad khat-ar hajar ki nongshong kulai, ïa kita, u la buh ha ki shnong buh kali, bad ryngkat bad u syiem ha Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u syiem u la pynlong ïa ka rupa bad ïa ka ksiar ha Jerusalem kum ki maw, bad ïa ki dieng Kedar u la pynlong kum ki dieng Dumbur kiba ha ri them, namar ba bun eh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki kulai kiba u Solomon u la don la wallam ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt; ki nongkhaïi u syiem ki la shim ïa ki da ki kynhun, kawei kawei ka kynhun ha la ka dor.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki la kyntiew artet, bad ki la wallam noh na Ijipt ïa ki kali hynriewspah shekel rupa kawei, bad uwei u kulai shispah sanphew: bad kumta, ïa ki syiem ki Hit baroh, bad ïa ki syiem ka Syria, ki la wallam ïa ki ha la ki kti."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Solomon u la thmu ban thaw kawei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai, bad kawei ka ïing na ka bynta ka hima jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Solomon u la ñiew hynñiewphew hajar ki briew ki ban kit jingkit, bad phraphew hajar kiba khet dieng ha ki lum, bad lai hajar hynriewspah ki ban khmih halor jong ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Solomon u la phah sha u Huram u syiem ka Tyros, u da ong, “Kumba me la leh bad u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad me la phah ha u ïa ki dieng Kedar ban thaw ka ïing ïa u ba un shong ha ka, kumta ruh, to leh bad nga.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ha khmih, nga thaw kawei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai uba U Blei jong nga, ban pynkyntang ïa ka sha u, bad ban thang ha khmat jong u, ïa ka jingiwbih thang da ki musla, bad na ka bynta u 'pu pyni uba ha la ka sngi, bad na ka bynta ka jingainguh thang mynstep bad ynda la janmiet, ha ki Sabbaton, bad ha ki bnai bathymmai, bad ha Ki Jingkhawai Niam ba la buh jong U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi. Kane ka long kaba ha la ka rta ïa ki Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka ïing kaba nga thaw ka long kaba khraw: namar U Blei jong ngi u long u bakhraw tam ïa ki blei baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, uei uba lah ban thaw ïing ïa u, haba ka bneng bad ka bneng jong ki bneng kim lah kynthup ïa u? nga long uei te, ba ngan thaw ïing ïa u, tang ban shu thang ïa ka jingiwbih ha khmat jong u?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te namar kata, to phah ha nga ïa u briew uba nang ban trei ksiar, bad rupa, bad rnong, bad nar, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka bajyrngam, bad uba nang ban pruid ïa ki laiphew rukom ka jingpruid, ban long lem bad ki riewstad kiba don bad nga ha ri Judah bad ha Jerusalem, ïa kiba u Dabid u kpa jong nga u la lah khreh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> To phah ruh ha nga ïa ki dieng Kedar, ki dieng Kseh, bad ki dieng Algum na Lebanon: naba nga tip ba ki shakri jong me ki nang ban khet dieng ha Lebanon; bad ha khmih, ki shakri jong nga kin long lem bad ki shakri jong me,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ïa ka ban khreh ïa nga shibun ki dieng keiñ: naba ka ïing kaba ngan sa thaw kan long kaba khraw ba-iphylla.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ha khmih, ngan ai ha ki shakri jong me, ki nongkhet kiba khet dieng, arphew hajar byrni u Kew ba la dung, bad arphew hajar byrni u Kew Barli, bad arphew hajar khra ka Waiñ, bad arphew hajar khra ka umphniang.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Huram u syiem ka Tyros u la phai ktien ha ka jingthoh, kaba u la phah sha u Solomon, “Namar ba U Trai u la ieit ïa ki briew jong U, U la pynlong syiem ïa me halor jong ki.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Huram u la ïai-ong shuh, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, uba la thaw ïa ka bneng bad ïa ka khyndew, uba la ai ha u syiem Dabid ïa u khun u bastad, uba la pyndap da ka jingstad bad ka jingshemphang, u ban thaw kawei ka ïing ïa U Trai, bad kawei ka ïing na ka bynta ka hima jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Te mynta, nga la phah ïa u briew u basian, uba don ka jingshemphang, u jong u Huram u kpa jong nga,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> u khun jong ka briew kaba na ki khun kynthei u Dan, bad u kpa jong u, u la long u briew uba na Tyros, uba nang ban trei ksiar, bad rupa, bad rnong, bad nar, bad maw, bad dieng, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka bajyrngam, bad ka jaiñ linen bani, bad ka basaw syng-iang; ban pruid ruh ïa kano kano ka kynja jingpruid, bad ban thaw buit ïa kano kano ka jingthaw buit: khnang ban buh jaka ïa u lem bad ki riewstad jong me, bad ki riewstad u kynrad jong nga u Dabid u kpa jong me.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te namar kata, ïa u Kew bad ïa u Kew Barli, ïa ka umphniang bad ïa ka Waiñ, shaphang kiba u kynrad jong nga u la kren, to un phah ha ki shakri jong u:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> te ngin khet dieng na Lebanon katba men donkam: bad ngin wallam ïa ka sha me da kaba pynkie ha ka duriaw shaduh Joppa; me ruh men sa kit ïa ka sha Jerusalem.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Solomon u la kheiñ ïa ki nongwei baroh kiba la don ha ka ri Israel katba kum ka jingkheiñ kaba u Dabid u kpa jong u, u la kheiñ ïa ki; bad la shem ïa ki shispah sanphew lai hajar bad hynriewspah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u la buh hynñiewphew hajar na ki ban kit ïa ki jingkit, bad phraphew hajar kiba la long ki nongkhet dieng ha ki lum, bad lai hajar bad hynriewspah ki sordar ki ban pyntrei ïa ki briew."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Solomon u la sdang ban tei ïa ka ïing U Trai ha Jerusalem halor u lum Moraïah, ha kaba U Trai u la paw ha u Dabid u kpa jong u, kaba u la khreh ha kata ka jaka kaba u Dabid u la buh, ha ka kyntem jong u Ornan u nong Jebus.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la sdang ban tei ha ka ba-ar tarik jong u bnai u ba-ar, ha ka basaw ka snem jong ka jingsynshar jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te kine ki long ki nongrim kiba u Solomon u la buh na ka bynta ban tei ïa ka ïing U Blei. Ka lynter ha ki pruh kat kum ka jingthew banyngkong ka la long hynriewphew pruh, bad ka pyngkiang, arphew pruh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ka batsha kaba la don ha khmat ka ïing, ka lynter jong ka, kajuh kat ka pyngkiang jong ka ïing, ka la long arphew pruh, bad ka jingjrong, shispah arphew: bad u la suit ïa ka na shapoh da ka ksiar banylla.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ïa ka ïing kaba kham khraw u la sop sad da u dieng Kseh, uba u la suit da ka ksiar ka babha, bad u la mutdur ha ka da ki dieng Tlai bad ki kynjri.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la pyndeng ïa ka ïing da ki maw bakordor na ka bynta ban itynnad: bad ka ksiar ka la long ka ksiar Parbaim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la suit ïa ka ïing ruh, ïa ki bim, ïa ki shawkad, bad ïa ki kynroh jong ka, bad ïa ki jingkhang jong ka, da ka ksiar; bad u la mutdur da ki Kherub halor ki kynroh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u la thaw ïa ka ïing bakyntang tam, ka lynter jong ka, kajuh kat ka pyngkiang jong ka ïing, ka la long arphew pruh, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, arphew pruh; bad u la suit ïa ka, da ka ksiar ka babha, kaba la leit haduh hynriewspah talent.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ka jingkhia ki prek, ka la long sanphew shekel ka ksiar. Bad u la suit ïa ki kamra kiba haneng, da ka ksiar.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad hapoh ka jaka bakyntang tam, u la thaw ar tylli ki Kherub da ka jingthaw dur; bad u la suit ïa ki, da ka ksiar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki thapniang jong ki Kherub ki la long kiba jrong arphew pruh: ka thapniang jong uwei u Kherub ka la long san pruh, ka da kot haduh ka kynroh jong ka ïing: bad kawei pat ka thapniang ka la long kumjuh, san pruh, ka da ïakynduh bad ka thapniang jong uta uwei u Kherub.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka thapniang jong uta uwei u Kherub, ka la long san pruh, ka da kot haduh ka kynroh jong ka ïing: bad kawei pat ka thapniang ruh, ka la long san pruh, ka da ïakynduh bad ka thapniang jong uwei pat u Kherub.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki thapniang jong kine ki Kherub ki la pynpyiar noh ïa lade, arphew pruh: bad ki la ïeng da la ki kjat, bad ki khmat jong ki, ki la long sha ka ïing.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u la thaw ïa ka jingkah na ka bajyrngam, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka jaiñ linen bani, bad u la mutdur halor da ki Kherub.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la thaw ruh ha khmat ka ïing ar tylli ki rishot kiba jrong laiphew san pruh, bad ka khlieh kaba la don ha ka kliar jong uwei pa uwei na ki, ka la long san pruh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u la thaw ki kynjri ha ka orakl, bad u la buh ha kliar jong ki rishot: bad u la thaw shispah tylli ki soh Pong, bad u la buh ïa ki halor kita ki kynjri.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u la pynïeng ïa ki rishot ha khmat ka templ, uwei sha kamon, bad uwei sha kadiang; bad u la khot kyrteng ïa uta uba sha kamon “u Jakhin”, bad ïa uta uba sha kadiang “u Boas”."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U la thaw ruh ka duwan rnong, arphew pruh ka lynter jong ka, bad arphew pruh ka pyngkiang jong ka, bad shiphew pruh ka jingjrong jong ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la thaw ruh ïa ka duriaw ba la saiñ, kaba shiphew pruh na rmiang sha rmiang, kaba pyllun sawdong, bad ka jingjrong jong ka, ka la long san pruh; bad u ksai uba laiphew pruh, u la kot baroh sawdong ïa ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te hapoh jong ka, la don kaba syriem ïa ki masi dab, kiba tawiar sawdong ïa ka, shiphew tylli shi pruh shi pruh, kiba tawiar sawdong ïa kata ka duriaw. Kita ki masi dab, ki la long ar kyrdan, kiba la saiñ haba la saiñ ïa ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ka la shong halor khat-ar tylli ki masi dab, lai tylli kiba khmih shatei, bad lai tylli kiba khmih sha sepngi, bad lai tylli kiba khmih shathie, bad lai tylli kiba khmih sha mihngi: bad ïa ka duriaw la pynshong halor jong ki haneng, bad ki bynta kiba shadien jong ki baroh ki la long shapoh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ka jingrben, ka la long shi khup; bad ïa ka rmiang jong ka, la thaw kum ka rmiang jong ka khuri, kum u syntiew Lili: ka la pdiang bad ka ngiam lai hajar bath.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la thaw ruh shiphew tylli ki dabor, bad u la buh san tylli sha kamon bad san tylli sha kadiang, ban sait ha ki; ïa kita kiei kiei kat kiba dei ha ka jingainguh thang ki sait ha kita: hynrei, ka duriaw ka la long ban sait ki lyngdoh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la thaw shiphew tylli ki dieng pynïeng sharak ksiar katba kum ka rukom shaphang jong ki; bad u la buh ïa ki ha ka templ, san tylli sha kamon, bad san tylli sha kadiang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U la thaw ruh shiphew tylli ki miej, bad u la buh ïa ki ha ka templ, san tylli sha ka krung kamon, bad san tylli sha kadiang. Bad u la thaw shispah tylli ki khuri ksiar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U la thaw shuh sa ka phyllaw jong ki lyngdoh, bad ka phyllaw kaba khraw, bad ki jingkhang ïa ka phyllaw, bad u la suit ïa ki jingkhang jong ki da ka rnong.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u la buh ïa ka duriaw sha ka krung kamon jong ka ïing shaphang mihngi, lam shathie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Huram u la thaw ïa ki khiew, bad ki siang, bad ki khuri. Kumta, u Huram u la pyndep ïa ka kam kaba u la trei ïa u syiem Solomon ha ka ïing U Blei:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ïa kita ki ar tylli ki rishot, bad ïa ki khuri, bad ïa ki ar tylli ki khlieh kiba la long ha kliar ki rishot; bad ïa ki ar tylli ki jingthain jar ban tap ïa kita ki ar tylli ki khuri jong ki khlieh kiba la long ha kliar ki rishot;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ïa ki sawspah ki soh Pong ïa kita ki ar tylli ki jingthain jar; ar kyrdan ki soh Pong ïa kawei kawei ka jingthain jar, ban tap ïa kita ki ar tylli ki khuri jong ki khlieh kiba la long halor ki rishot.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U la thaw ruh ki jingpynshong, bad u la thaw ïa ki dabor halor kita ki jingpynshong;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ïa kawei ka duriaw, bad khat-ar tylli ki masi dab hapoh jong ka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ïa ki khiew ruh, bad ki siang, bad ki bnoh doh, bad ki kynja pliang jong ka baroh, u Huram uba u kpa jong u, u la thaw na ka bynta u syiem Solomon ïa ka ïing U Trai da ka rnong baphyrnai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ha ka madan Jordan, u syiem u la saiñ ïa ki, ha ka 'dewbyrtha hapdeng ka Sukkoth bad ka Seredah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumne shikatdei eh, u Solomon u la thaw ïa kine ki kynja pliang baroh: naba ïa ka jingkhia ka rnong ym lah shem shuh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Solomon u la thaw ïa ki kynja pliang baroh kiba la don ha ka ïing U Blei, ïa ka duwan ksiar ruh, bad ïa ki miej ha kiba la don u 'pu pyni;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ïa ki dieng pynïeng sharak lem bad ki sharak jong ki, ba kin thang kat kum ka rukom ha khmat ka orakl, da ka ksiar banylla;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ïa ki syntiew, bad ïa ki sharak, bad ïa ki nap, da ka ksiar, bad kata ka ksiar banylla;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ïa ki jinglur sharak, bad ïa ki khuri, bad ki siang, bad ki pliang ding, da ka ksiar banylla: bad ka khyrdop jong ka ïing, ki jingkhang ba kham shapoh jong ka na ka bynta ka jaka bakyntang tam, bad ïa ki jingkhang jong ka ïing, kata, ki jong ka templ, ki la long da ka ksiar."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kumta, ka kam baroh ba u Solomon u la leh ïa ka ïing U Trai ka la dep. Bad u Solomon u la wallam shapoh ïa kiei kiei kiba u Dabid u kpa jong u, u la pynkyntang; ïa ka rupa, bad ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ki kynja pliang baroh keiñ, bad u la buh ïa ki ha ki jaka kynshew ka ïing U Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u Solomon u la ïalum lang ïa ki tymmen basan ki Israel bad ïa ki nongïalam jong ki jaid, ïa ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa ki khun Israel, ha Jerusalem, ban wallam artet ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai na ka shnong u Dabid, kaba long ka Seïon.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki paidbah Israel baroh ki la ïalum lang ha u syiem ha ka jingkhawai, kaba la long ha u bnai u bahynñiew.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad baroh ki tymmen basan ki Israel ki la wan, bad ki Lebi ki la bah ïa ka synduk.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki la wallam artet ïa ka synduk, bad ïa Ka Ïingjaiñ Ka Jingïaseng, bad ïa ki kynja pliang bakhuid baroh kiba ha kata ka ïingjaiñ; ïa kine, ki lyngdoh ki Lebi ki la wallam artet.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u syiem Solomon bad ki paidlang Israel baroh, kiba la ïalum lang ha u, ki la don ha khmat ka synduk, ki da ïakñia langbrot bad masi dab, ki bym lah ong lane ñiew ba bun than eh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki lyngdoh ki la wallam ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai sha la ka jaka, hapoh ka orakl jong ka ïing, ha ka jaka kyntang tam, hapoh ki thapniang ki Kherub keiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Naba ki Kherub ki pyiar ïa la ki thapniang halor ka jaka ka synduk bad ki Kherub ki la tap ïa kata ka synduk bad ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka nalor.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad kita ki dieng jingbah ki long kiba jrong ba lah ban ïohi ïa ki tduh jong kita ki dieng jingbah na ka synduk ha khmat ka orakl; hynrei, ym ïohi ïa ki na shabar: bad hangta ka don, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ym don ei ei hapoh ka synduk nalor ki ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap kiba u Moses u la buh hangta ha Horeb, mynba U Trai u la pynlong ka jutang bad ki khun Israel, haba ki la mih noh na Ijipt.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ki lyngdoh ki la mih noh na ka jaka kyntang, (naba ki lyngdoh baroh kiba la don hangta, ki la lah pynkyntang ïa lade, bad kim shym la sumar la ki jingïakylliang jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki Lebi ruh kiba la long ki nongrwai, baroh na ki, u Asaph, u Heman, u Jeduthun, bad ki khun jong ki bad ki para jong ki keiñ, ki la kup da ka jaiñ linen bani, bad ki ksing padiah bad ki nebel bad ki duitara, ki la ïeng ha ki dong kaba shaphang mihngi jong ka duwan, bad ryngkat bad ki shispah arphew ngut ki lyngdoh kiba put ronsing:)",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> te haba ki nongput ronsing bad kiba rwai ki la ïalong kum kawei, ban pynsngew tang kawei ka jingsawa ha kaba ïaroh bad kaba ainguh ha U Trai; bad haba ki la pynjam ïa la ka jingkynud da ki ronsing bad ki ksing padiah bad ki tiar rwai, bad ba ki la ïaroh ïa U Trai, ki ïa-ong: “Naba u long u babha; naba ka jingisynei jong u ka neh junom:” Hangta te ïa ka ïing la pyndap da u lyoh, ïa ka ïing U Trai keiñ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Katba ki lyngdoh kim lah ïeng shuh ban shakri namar uta u lyoh: naba ka burom U Trai ka la pyndap ïa ka ïing U Blei."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Solomon u la kren, “U Trai u la ong ba un shong ha ka jingdum batliw tliw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, nga la tei ka ïing ïa me ban shong, bad ka jaka ïa me ban shong junom.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Syiem u la phai la ka khmat, bad u la kyrkhu ïa u paidbah Israel baroh: bad u paidbah Israel baroh u ïeng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la ong, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, uba la kren da la ka shyntur ha u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad da la ka kti u la pyndep ïa ka, u da ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ‘Naduh kata ka sngi ba nga la wallam noh ïa u paidbah jong nga na ka ri Ijipt, ngam shym la jied ïa kano kano ka nongbah na ki jaid Israel baroh ban tei ïing ha ka, ba ka kyrteng jong nga kan ïoh long hangta; lymne ngam shym la jied ïa uno uno u briew ban long u nongïalam halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> hynrei, nga la jied ïa ka Jerusalem, ba ka kyrteng jong nga kan ïoh long hangta: bad nga la jied ïa u Dabid ban long halor u paidbah jong nga ki Israel.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka la don ha ka dohnud u Dabid u kpa jong nga ban tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai U Blei ki Israel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la ong ha u Dabid u kpa jong nga, “Kumba ka la don ha ka dohnud jong me ban tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, me la leh bha keiñ ba kane ka la don ha ka dohnud jong me:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> la kumta ruh, men ym tei ïa kata ka ïing; hynrei, u khun jong me u ban sa mih noh na ka syngkai jong me, uta un tei ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng jong nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad U Trai u la pyndep ïa la ka ktien ba u la kren: namar nga la ïeng ha ka jaka u Dabid u kpa jong nga, bad nga shong ha ka khet Israel, kumba U Trai u la kular, bad nga la tei ïa kata ka ïing ïa ka kyrteng U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad hangta nga la buh ïa ka synduk, ha kaba don ka jutang U Trai, ïa kaba u la pynlong bad ki khun Israel.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u la ïeng ha khmat ka duwan U Trai ha khmat u paidbah Israel baroh, bad u la rah la ki kti:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> (naba u Solomon u la shna ka rynsan rnong, ka lynter, san pruh, bad ka pyngkiang, san pruh, bad ka jingjrong, lai pruh, bad u la pynïeng ïa ka hapdeng ka phyllaw; bad u la ïeng halor jong ka, bad u la dem khohsiew ha khmat u paidbah Israel baroh, bad u la rah la ki kti sha bneng:)",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u la ong, “A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ym don U Blei uba kat ma me, ha bneng, lane ha ka khyndew; uba sumar ïa ka jutang bad ka jingisynei bad la ki shakri, kiba ïaid ha khmat jong me da ka dohnud jong ki baroh;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> uba la sumar bad u shakri jong me u Dabid u kpa jong nga ïa kata kaba me la kular ha u; shisha, me la kren da la ka shyntur, bad me la pyndep ïa ka da la ka kti, kumba ka long ha kane ka sngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar kata te, A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, to sumar ïa kata kaba me la kular bad u shakri jong me u Dabid u kpa jong nga, me da ong, ‘Kan ym duh briew ïa me ha khmat jong nga ban shong halor ka khet Israel; tangba ki khun jong me kin sumar la ka ïaid ka ïeng, ban ïaid ha ka hukum jong nga, kumba me ruh, me la ïaid ha khmat jong nga.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te namar kata, A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ai ba yn pynshisha ïa ka ktien jong me ïa kaba me la kren ha u Dabid u shakri jong me.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Hynrei, shisha shisha U Blei un shong sah ma bad ki briew ha ka khyndew? Ha khmih, ka bneng bad ka bneng jong ki bneng kam lah ban kynthup ïa me; sa ine i ïing lei lei iba nga la tei!",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> La kumta ruh, to khmih ïa ka jingduwai u shakri jong me, bad ïa ka jingkyrpad jong u, A Trai U Blei jong nga, ban shahshkor ïa ka jingpyrta bad ka jingduwai kaba u shakri jong me u duwai ha khmat jong me:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ba ki khmat jong me kin peit sha kane ka ïing mynsngi bad mynmiet, sha ka jaka ïa kaba me la ong ba men buh la ka kyrteng hangta; ban sngap ïa ka jingduwai ba u shakri jong me un duwai sha kane ka jaka.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad to sngap ïa ki jingkyrpad u shakri jong me, bad ki jong ki briew jong me ki Israel, haba kin duwai sha kane ka jaka: shisha, to sngap ma me na ka jaka shong jong me, na bneng hi keiñ; bad haba me sngew, to map.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Lada u briew u leh pop ïa la u paramarjan, bad ba la buh ka jingsmai halor jong u ïa ka ban pynsmai ïa u, bad u wan ban smai ha khmat ka duwan jong me ha kane ka ïing,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ynda kumta, to sngap ma me na bneng, bad to leh, bad to bishar ïa la ki shakri, da pynhiar kput ïa u bymman, ban pynhap ïa ka lynti jong u halor ka khlieh jong u; bad da pynksan ïa u bahok, ban ai ha u katba kum ka hok jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Bad lada la shoh jop ïa ki Israel ki briew jong me ha khmat u nongshun, namar ba ki la leh pop ïa me; bad ba kin phai pat bad ba kin phla ïa ka kyrteng jong me, bad ba kin duwai bad kin kyrpad ha khmat jong me ha kane ka ïing:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> te to sngap ma me na bneng, bad to map ïa ka pop ki briew jong me ki Israel, bad to wallam pat ïa ki sha ka ri kaba me la ai ha ki bad ha ki kpa jong ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Haba la set khop ïa ka bneng, bad ym hap slap shuh, namar ba ki la leh pop ïa me; lada ki duwai sha kane ka jaka, bad ki phla ïa ka kyrteng jong me, bad ki kylla na la ka pop, haba me pynshitom ïa ki:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> te to sngap ma me na bneng, bad to map ïa ka pop ki shakri jong me, bad ïa ka jong ki briew jong me ki Israel, haba me hikai ïa ki, ïa ka lynti babha ha kaba ki dei ban ïaid; bad to phah ïa u slap ha la ka ri, kaba me la ai ha la ki briew ban long ka ri kynti.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Lada jia 'nemsniew ha ka ri, lada jia ka jingïapkhlam, lada jia kaba ïap-ïong lane kaba bthuh, u puit kluiñ lane u puit khlam; lada ki nongshun jong ki, ki ker kut ïa ki ha ka ri ki khyrdop jong ki; la kano kano ka jingïapthem lane kano kano ka jingpang kaba don;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> kano kano ka jingduwai bad ka jingkyrpad ba pynlong da uno uno u briew, lane da ki briew jong me baroh ki Israel, uba tip marwei marwei ïa la ka jong ka jingshitom bad la ka jong ka jingsngewsih, bad un kner la ki kti sha kane ka ïing:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> te to sngap ma me na bneng ka jaka shong jong me, bad to map, bad ai ha uwei uwei baroh katba kum ki lynti jong u baroh, uba ka dohnud jong u me tip; (namar ma me, tang ma me hi, me ithuh ïa ki dohnud ki khun bynriew;)",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ba kin dup sheptieng ïa me, ban ïaid ha ki lynti jong me, katba ki dang im ha ka ri kaba me la ai ha ki kpa jong ngi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Shaphang u nongwei ruh, u bymlong na ki briew jong me ki Israel, haba u wan na ka ri kaba jngai na ka bynta ka kyrteng bakhraw jong me, bad ka kti badonbor jong me, bad ka ksang'ti ba la kner jong me; haba kin wan duwai sha kane ka ïing:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> te to sngap ma me na bneng, na ka jaka shong jong me keiñ, bad to leh baroh katba kum ka jingkyrpad uta u nongwei ha me; ba ki kynja bynriew ka khyndew baroh kin tip ïa ka kyrteng jong me, bad kin sheptieng ïa me, kumba leh ki briew jong me ki Israel, bad ba kin tip ba ïa kane ka ïing ba nga la tei, la khot da ka kyrteng jong me.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Lada ki briew jong me ki leit ïaleh thma ïa ki nongshun jong ki, da kano kano ka lynti ba men phah ïa ki, bad kin duwai ha me sha kane ka shnong kaba me la jied, bad sha ka ïing kaba nga la tei ïa ka kyrteng jong me:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> te to sngap ma me na bneng ïa ka jingduwai jong ki, bad ïa ka jingkyrpad jong ki, bad to pynïeng ïa ka hok jong ki.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Lada ki leh pop ïa me, (naba ym don u bym ju leh pop,) bad me bitar ïa ki, bad me ai noh ïa ki ha u nongshun, haduh ba u ring mraw ïa ki sha ka ri kaba jngai eh lane kaba jan;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> pynban, lada kin pyrkhat ïa lade ha kata ka ri sha kaba la ring mraw ïa ki, bad ki phai pat, bad kin kyrpad ha me ha ka ri ka jinglongmraw jong ki, ki ïa-ong, ‘Ngi la leh pop, ngi la leh mutlop eh, bad ngi la leh bymman;’",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> lada kin phai sha me da la ka dohnud baroh bad da la ka mynsiem baroh ha ka ri ka jinglongmraw jong ki, sha kaba ki la ring mraw ïa ki, bad ki duwai sha la ka ri, ïa kaba me la ai ha ki kpa jong ki, bad kane ka nongbah ïa kaba me la jied, bad sha kane ka ïing ïa kaba nga la tei ïa ka kyrteng jong me:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> te to sngap ma me na bneng, na ka jaka shong jong me keiñ, ïa ka jingduwai jong ki bad ïa ki jingkyrpad jong ki, bad to pynïeng ïa ka hok jong ki: bad to map ïa ki briew jong me kiba la leh pop ïa me.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Mynta, A U Blei jong nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, to peit la ki khmat, bad to pynshah la ki shkor ha ki jingduwai ba la pynlong ha kane ka jaka.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> “Namar kata te, to ïeng, A Trai U Blei, sha ka jaka shongthait jong me, ma me, bad ka synduk ka bor jong me: A Trai U Blei, ai ban pynkup ïa ki lyngdoh jong me da ka jingpynim, bad to ki riewkhuid jong me kin leh kmen ha ka jingbha.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> A Trai U Blei, wat pynphai noh ïa ka khmat jong uba la sleh jong me: to kynmaw ïa ki jingisynei u Dabid u shakri jong me.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u Solomon u la lah pynkut ïa kaba duwai, ka ding ka la hiar na bneng, bad ka la bam duh ïa ka jingainguh thang bad ïa ki jingkñia; bad ka burom U Trai ka la pyndap ïa ka ïing.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki lyngdoh kim lah ban rung hapoh ka ïing U Trai, namar ka burom U Trai ka la pyndap ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te baroh ki khun Israel ki la ïakhmih, haba ka ding ka la hiar, bad ba ka burom U Trai ka la long halor ka ïing; bad ki la dem ngon la ki khmat ha ka khyndew halor ka jingsiang, bad ki la mane, bad ki la ainguh ha U Trai, ki ïa-ong, “Namar u long u babha; namar ka jingisynei jong u ka neh ha la ka rta.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hadien kata, u syiem bad u paidbah baroh, ki la ainguh ka jingkñia ha khmat U Trai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la ai ka jingkñia arphew ar hajar ki masi dab, bad shispah arphew hajar ki langbrot. Kumta, u syiem bad ki paidbah baroh, ki la pynkyntang ïa ka ïing U Blei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki lyngdoh ki la ïeng, katba kum ki kam jong ki; ki Lebi ruh bad ki tiar rwai jong U Trai, ïa kiba u syiem Dabid u la lah thaw ban ainguh ha U Trai, namar ka jingisynei jong u ka neh ha la ka rta, haba u Dabid u la ïaroh da ka jingshakri jong ki: te ki lyngdoh ki la put turoi ha khmat jong ki; te ki Israel baroh ki la ïeng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nalor kata, u Solomon u la pynkyntang ïa ka pdeng jong ka phyllaw kaba la don ha khmat ka ïing U Trai; namar hangta u la ainguh ïa ka jingainguh thang, bad ïa ka khleiñ jong ki jingainguh bapynïasuk: namar ka duwan rnong ïa kaba u Solomon u la lah thaw kam lah ban ngiam ïa ka jingainguh thang, bad ïa ka jingainguh bam, bad ïa ka khleiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, u Solomon u la rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam ha kata ka por, hynñiew sngi, bad ki Israel baroh lem bad u, ka jingïalang bakhraw eh, naduh ka jingbsut sha Hamath haduh ka wah rit jong ka Ijipt.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ha ka sngi ka baphra ki la pynlong ka jingïaseng bakyntang: namar ki la rakhe ïa ka jingpynkyntang ïa ka duwan, hynñiew sngi, bad ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam, hynñiew sngi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ha ka ba-arphew lai ka sngi jong u bnai u bahynñiew, u la phah noh ïa ki paidbah sha ki ïingjaiñ jong ki, ba la kmen bad ba la sngewbha la ka dohnud namar ka jingbha ïa kaba U Trai u la lah leh ha u Dabid, bad ha u Solomon, bad ha ki Israel ki briew jong U.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumne u Solomon u la pyndep ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ka ïingsyiem: bad baroh kaba la poi ha ka dohnud u Solomon ban thaw hapoh ka ïing U Trai, bad hapoh ka ïing jong u hi, u la thaw bha.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te U Trai u la paw ha u Solomon mynmiet, bad u la ong ha u, “Nga la ïohsngew ïa ka jingduwai jong me, bad nga la jied ïa kane ka jaka ha lade ban long ka ïing jingkñia.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lada nga khang khop ïa ka bneng ba yn ym don slap, lane lada nga hukum ïa u puit ban bam duh ïa ka ri, lane lada nga phah ïa ka ïapkhlam hapdeng ki briew jong nga;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> lada ki briew jong nga, ïa kiba la khot da ka kyrteng jong nga, kin pynrit ïa lade, bad kin duwai, bad kin wad ïa ka khmat jong nga, bad kin phai noh na ki lynti bymman jong ki; kumta te ngan sngew na bneng, bad ngan map ïa ki pop jong ki, bad ngan pynkhiah ïa ka ri jong ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki khmat jong nga kin peit, bad ki shkor jong nga kin sngap ha ka jingduwai ka ban pynlong ha kane ka jaka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar mynta nga la jied bad nga la pynkyntang kyntang ïa kane ka ïing, ba ka kyrteng jong nga ka lah ban long hangta ha la ka rta: bad ki khmat jong nga bad ka dohnud jong nga kin long hangta junom.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te shaphang jong me, lada men ïaid ha khmat jong nga kumba u Dabid u kpa jong me u la ïaid, bad men leh ïa baroh kat kaba nga la hukum ïa me, bad men sumar ïa ki aiñ jong nga bad ïa ki jingbishar jong nga;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> nga te ngan pynskhem ïa ka khet ka hima jong me, kumba nga la teh jutang bad u Dabid u kpa jong me, nga da ong, ‘Yn ym duh u briew ïa me ban long nongsynshar ha Israel.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Hynrei, lada phi phai lyndet, bad phin iehnoh ïa ki aiñ jong nga bad ïa ki hukum jong nga ïa kiba nga la buh ha khmat jong phi, bad phin leit shakri ïa kiwei pat ki blei, bad mane ïa ki:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hangta te ngan rat noh ïa ki naduh tynrai, na ka ri jong nga ïa kaba nga la ai ha ki; bad ïa kane ka ïing, ïa kaba nga la pynkyntang ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, ngan kyntait noh na khmat jong nga, bad ngan pynlong ïa ka jingkynnohbeiñ bad ka jingkynshi hapdeng ki kynja bynriew baroh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ïa kane ka ïing, kaba jrong katta katta, uwei uwei baroh uba ïaid lait ïa ka un kyndit thred, bad un ong, ‘Balei U Trai u la leh kumne ïa kane ka ri, bad ïa kane ka ïing?’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te kin ïathuh, ‘Namar ba ki la lyndet ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki, uba la wallam noh ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt, bad ki la bat ïa kiwei pat ki blei, bad ki la mane ïa ki, bad ki la shakri ïa ki: namar kata keiñ, u la wallam ïa kane ka jingsniew baroh halor jong ki.’ ”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka bakut arphew snem, ha kaba u Solomon u la lah tei ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa la ka jong ka ïing,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ïa ki shnong ïa kiba u Huram u la lah ai ha u Solomon, u Solomon u la tei ïa ki, bad u la pynshong ïa ki khun Israel ha ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Solomon u la leit sha Hamath-sobah, bad u la jop ïa ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la tei ïa ka Tadmor ha ka ri khlaw, bad ïa ki shnong jingkynshew baroh, ïa kiba u la tei ha Hamath.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la tei ruh ïa ka Beth-horon ba haneng, bad ïa ka Beth-horon ba harum, ki nongbah ba la ker kut da ki kynroh, ki khyrdop, bad ki dieng jingkhang;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ïa ka Baalath, bad ïa ki nongbah jingkynshew baroh kiba u Solomon u la don, bad ïa ki nongbah baroh ïa ki kali jong u, bad ïa ki nongbah baroh ïa ki nongshong kulai jong u, bad ïa baroh ba u Solomon u la kwah ban tei sngewbha ha Jerusalem, bad ha Lebanon, bad ha ka ri baroh ka jingsynshar jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Shaphang kita ki briew baroh ïa kiba la pynsah na ki Hit, bad ki Amor, bad ki Peris, bad ki Hib, bad ki Jebus, ki bymlong na Israel;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ki khun jong ki, kiba la sah hadien jong ki ha ka ri, ïa kiba ki khun Israel kim shym la pynduh noh, na kine, u Solomon u la pynmih ki khar paid kum ki mraw, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, na ki khun Israel, u Solomon um shym la pynlong shakri ïa ka jingtrei jong u; hynrei, ki la long ki nongïapom, bad ki rangbah jong ki kaptan jong u, bad ki rangbah ki kali jong u bad jong ki nongshong kulai jong u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kine ki la long ki shakri rangbah u syiem Solomon, arspah sanphew keiñ, kiba la synshar halor ki paidbah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Solomon u la wallam ïa ka khun u Pharaoh na ka nongbah u Dabid sha ka ïing ba u la tei na ka bynta jong ka: namar u la ong, “Ka tnga jong nga kan ym shong ha ka ïing jong u Dabid u syiem ki Israel, namar kita ki jaka ki long ki bakyntang, ha kiba ka synduk ka jutang jong U Trai ka la wan.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, u Solomon u la ainguh ki jingainguh thang ha U Trai halor ka duwan U Trai, ïa kaba u la tei ha khmat kata ka batsha,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> kumba ka dei ka kam jong kawei kawei ka sngi, u da ainguh katba kum ka hukum u Moses, ha ki Sabbaton, bad ha ki bnai bathymmai, bad ha Ki Jingkhawai Niam ba la buh, lai sien shi snem, ha Ka Jingkhawai Niam U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat, bad ha Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ki Taïew, bad ha Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ki Ïingtrep.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u la buh, katba kum ka hukum u Dabid u kpa jong u, ïa ki jingkylliang sngi jong ki lyngdoh, ïa ka jingshakri jong ki, bad ïa ki Lebi ha ki jingsumar jong ki, ban ïaroh, bad ban shakri ha khmat ki lyngdoh, kumba ka dei ka kam kawei kawei ka sngi: ïa ki nongsumar jingkhang ruh ha la ki jingkylliang sngi ha ka khyrdop baroh: naba kumta u Dabid u briew jong U Blei u la hukum.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kim shym la kynriah noh na ka hukum jong u syiem ïa ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi shaphang kano kano ka kam, lane shaphang ki jingkynshew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ïa ka kam u Solomon baroh la khreh haduh ka sngi ka jingpynshong nongrim ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad tad ynda la pyndep ïa ka. Kumta, ïa ka ïing U Trai la pynjanai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hadien kata, u Solomon u la leit sha Esion-geber, bad sha Eloth, harud duriaw ha ka ri Edom.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Huram u la phah ïa u ki lieng, bad ki shakri kiba nang shaphang ka duriaw, da ki kti ki shakri jong u; te ki la wan bad ki shakri u Solomon sha Ophir, bad ki la wallam nangta sawspah sanphew talent ka ksiar, bad ki la wallam ïa ki ha u syiem Solomon."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba ka syiem Sheba ka la ïohsngew ïa ka nam u Solomon, ka la wan ban tynjuh ïa u Solomon da ki jingkylli ba-eh ha Jerusalem, bad shibun bah ki nongbud, bad ki ut kiba la kit ki masla, bad ka ksiar shibun, bad ki mawkordor: te haba ka la poi ha u Solomon, ka la ïakren bad u shaphang baroh kaba la don ha ka dohnud jong ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Solomon u la ïathuh ha ka, ïa ki jingkylli jong ka baroh: bad ym shym la don kano kano kaba rieh na u Solomon ïa kaba um shym la ïathuh ha ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba ka syiem Sheba ka la lah ïohi ïa ka jingstad u Solomon, bad ïa ka ïing ïa kaba u la lah tei,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ïa ka jingbam ha ka miej jong u, bad kaba shong ki shakri jong u, bad kaba ïeng ki myntri jong u, bad ki jingriam jong ki, bad ïa ki nongrah khuri jong u ruh, bad ïa ki jingriam jong ki; bad ïa ka lynti jong u da kaba u leit kiew sha ka ïing U Trai; ym don mynsiem shuh ha ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ka la ong ha u syiem, “Ka long ka jingbna bashisha kaba nga la ïohsngew ha la ka ri hi shaphang ki kam jong me, bad ka jingstad jong me.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, ngam shym la ngeit ïa ki ktien jong ki, tad ynda nga la wan, bad ki khmat jong nga ki la ïohi ïa ka: te ha khmih, kaba shiteng ruh na ka jingkhraw ka jingstad jong me ym shym la ïathuh ïa nga: me palat ïa ka nam kaba nga la ïohsngew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Suk ki briew jong me, bad suk kine ki shakri jong me, kiba ïeng ha la ka sngi ha khmat jong me, bad kiba ïohsngew ïa ka jingstad jong me.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai U Blei jong me, uba la ieit ïa me, ban buh ïa me halor ka khet jong u, ban long syiem na ka bynta U Trai U Blei jong me: namar ba U Blei jong me u la ieit ïa ki Israel, ban pynskhem ïa ki ha la ka rta, namar kata, u la pynlong ïa me u syiem halor jong ki, ban leh ïa ka jingbishar bad ïa ka hok.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ka la ai ïa u syiem shispah arphew talent ka ksiar, bad ki masla shikatdei eh, bad ki mawkordor: lymne ym ju don kum uta u masla kum uba ka syiem Sheba ka la ai ha u syiem Solomon.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki shakri u Huram ruh, bad ki shakri u Solomon, kiba la wallam ka ksiar na Ophir, ki la wallam ki dieng Algum bad ki mawkordor.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u syiem u la thaw na kita ki dieng Algum, ki rynsan ïa ka ïing U Trai bad ïa ka ïing u syiem, bad ïa ki duitara bad ki nebel ïa ki nongrwai: bad ym shym la ïohi kum kita mynshuwa ha ka ri Judah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la ai ha ka syiem Sheba ïa ka jingkwah jong ka baroh, ïa kaei kaei kat kaba ka la pan, nalor kata kaba ka la lah wallam ha u syiem. Kumta, ka la leit wan noh, bad ka la leit sha la ka ri, ma ka bad ki shakri jong ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ka jingkhia ka ksiar kaba la wan ha u Solomon shi snem ka la long hynriewspah hynriewphew hynriew talent ksiar;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> nalor kata kaba ki nongkhaïi bad ki mahajon ki la wallam: bad baroh ki syiem ka Arabia bad ki lyngskor jong ka ri ki la wallam ka ksiar bad ka rupa ha u Solomon.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u syiem Solomon u la thaw arspah ki 'tiehbah da ka ksiar ba shu shoh; hynriewspah shekel ka ksiar ba shu shoh ka la leit ha kawei ka 'tiehbah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u la thaw laispah ki stieh da ka ksiar ba shu shoh; laispah shekel ka ksiar ka la leit ha kawei ka stieh: te u syiem u la buh ïa ki ha ka ïing jong ka khlaw Lebanon.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nalor kata, u syiem u la thaw ka khet bniat hati kaba khraw, bad u la suit ïa ka, da ka ksiar banylla.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad kata ka khet ka la don hynriew kyrdan, bad ka jingïuh kjat ksiar, ïa kiba la pyndait ha ka khet, bad ki jingshan baroh ar liang hajan ka jaka shong, bad ar tylli ki sing kiba ïeng hajan ki jingshan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad khat-ar ki sing ki la ïeng hangta baroh ar liang halor ki hynriew kyrdan: ym ju thaw kum kata ha kano kano ka hima.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad baroh ki khuri dih u syiem Solomon, ki la long da ka ksiar; bad baroh ki khiew ki pliang jong ka ïing jong ka khlaw Lebanon, ki la long da ka ksiar nylla: ïa ka rupa ym shym ñiewkor ei ei ha ki sngi u Solomon.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Naba u syiem u la don ki lieng kiba leit sha Tarshish bad ki shakri u Huram: shi sien ha ka lai snem ki lieng Tarshish ki ju wan, kiba wallam ksiar, bad rupa, ka bniat hati, bad ki huleng, bad ki klew.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, u syiem Solomon u la palat ïa ki syiem baroh jong ka khyndew ha ka spah bad ka jingstad.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te baroh ki syiem jong ka pyrthei, ki la wad ïa ka khmat u Solomon, ban ïohsngew ïa ka jingstad jong u, ïa kaba U Blei u la buh ha ka dohnud jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki la ïawallam u briew baroh la ka jingai sngewbha, ki pliang rupa, bad ki pliang ksiar, bad ka jaiñkup, ka jingkieng atiar, bad ki masla, ki kulai, bad ki khashor, da ka jingkheiñ man la ka snem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Solomon u la don saw hajar ki pulit ïa ki kulai bad ki kali ïapom, bad khat-ar hajar ki nongshong kulai, ïa kiba u la buh ha ki shnong ri kali, bad lem bad u syiem ha Jerusalem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u la synshar halor ki syiem baroh naduh ka Wah jin haduh ka ri ki Philistia, bad haduh rud Ijipt.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u syiem u la pynlong ïa ka rupa ha Jerusalem kum ki maw, bad ïa ki dieng Kedar u la pynlong kum ki dieng Dumbur kiba ha ka ri them, namar ba bun eh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ki la wallam kulai ïa u Solomon na ka ri Ijipt, bad na ki ri baroh.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Solomon, ki banyngkong bad bakhatduh, hato ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Jingïathuh u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa, bad ha Ka Jingïathuhlypa u Ahijah u nong Shilon, bad ha Ki Jingithuhpaw u Iddo u nongïohi shaphang u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Solomon u la synshar ha Jerusalem halor ki Israel baroh, sawphew snem.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te u Solomon u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid u kpa jong u: bad u Rehoboam u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Rehoboam u la leit sha Shekhem; namar baroh ki Israel ki la poi ha Shekhem ban pynlong syiem ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat u la ïohsngew ïa kata, (namar u la don ha Ijipt, sha kaba u la phet ïap na khmat u syiem Solomon,) u Jeroboam u la wan phai noh na ri Ijipt.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la phah khot ïa u; bad u Jeroboam bad ki Israel baroh ki la ïawan, bad ki la ïakren ha u Rehoboam, ki ïa-ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “U Kpa jong me u la pynlong khia ïa ka lyngkor jong ngi: mynta te to men kham pynsting ïa ka jingpyntrei khia u kpa jong me, bad ïa ka lyngkor bakhia kaba u la pynkit ha ngi, te ngin shakri ïa me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “To wan pat sa lai sngi ha nga.” Te u paidbah u la leit noh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u syiem Rehoboam u la ïapyrkhat bad ki tymmen, kiba la ju ïeng ha khmat u Solomon u kpa jong u katba u dang im, u da ong, “Kumno phi pyni ïa nga ba ngan ai jubab ha une u paidbah?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki te ki la kren ha u, ki ïa-ong, “Lada me leh sbun ha une u paidbah, bad men pynsngewbha ïa ki, bad men kren ki ktien bha ha ki, ki ruh kin long ki shakri jong me junom.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, u la lyndet ïa ka jingpyni ki tymmen kaba ki la ai ha u, bad u la ïapyrkhat bad ki samla kiba ïasan ryngkat bad u, kiba ju ïeng ha khmat jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Kumno phi pyni ba ngin ai jubab ha une u paidbah uba la kren ha nga, u da ong, ‘To kham pynsting ïa ka lyngkor kaba u kpa jong me u la pynkit ha ngi’?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki samla kiba la ïasan ryngkat bad u ki la kren ha u, ki ïa-ong, “Kumne men kren ha une u paidbah uba la kren ha me, da kaba ong, ‘U kpa jong me uba la pynkhia ïa ka lyngkor jong ngi, hynrei, to kham pynsting ma me ïa ka ha ngi’; kumne men ong ha ki, ‘Ka 'tiduh jong nga ka kham heh ban ïa ka syngkai u kpa jong nga.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te mynta, kumba u kpa jong nga u la pynkit ïa phi da ka lyngkor bakhia, ngan nang pyntam shuh ha ka lyngkor jong phi: u kpa jong nga u la pynshitom ïa phi da ki dieng sympat, hynrei, ngan pynshitom da ki shabuk.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, u Jeroboam bad u paidbah baroh ki la wan ha u Rehoboam, ha ka balai sngi, kumba u syiem u la hukum, u da ong, “Sa wan pat ha nga ha ka sngi ka balai.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u syiem u la phai ktien da kaba eh ha ki; bad u syiem Rehoboam u la kyntait ïa ka jingpyni ki tymmen,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad u la kren ha ki kat kum ka jingpyni ki samla, u da ong, “U kpa jong nga u la pynkhia ïa ka lyngkor jong phi, hynrei, ngan nang pyntam shuh ha ka: u kpa jong nga u la pynshitom ïa phi da ki dieng sympat, hynrei, ngan pynshitom da ki shabuk.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, u syiem um shym shahshkor ha u paidbah; namar ka la long kaba la pynjia da U Blei, ba U Trai un ïoh pynskhem ïa la ka ktien, kaba u la kren da ka kti u Ahijah u nong Shilon ha u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba ki Israel baroh ki la ïohi ba u syiem um shahshkor ïa ki, u paidbah u la ïathuh ha u syiem, u da ong, “Ka bynta aïu ngi don ha u Dabid? lymne ngim don jingïoh bynta ei ei ha u khun u Jesse: man la u briew sha la ki ïingjaiñ, ko Israel: mynta te, khmih hi ïa la ka ïing, ko Dabid.” Kumta, baroh ki Israel ki la leit noh sha la ki ïingjaiñ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, kita ki khun Israel kiba shong ha ki shnong Judah, u Rehoboam u la synshar halor jong ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u syiem Rehoboam u la phah ïa u Hadoram, uba halor ka khajna; bad ki khun Israel ki la lynthem ïa u da ki maw, te u la ïap. Bad u syiem Rehoboam u la pynkloi ban kiew ha la ka kali, ïa ka ban phet sha Jerusalem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, ki Israel ki la ïaleh pyrshah ïa ka ïing u Dabid, haduh kane ka sngi."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad haba u Rehoboam u la wan poi sha Jerusalem, u la lum lang ïa ka ïing Judah bad Benjamin, shispah phraphew hajar ki rangbah ba la kynsai, kiba la long ki nongïapom, ban ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel, ban pynphai pat ïa ka hima sha u Rehoboam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Shemaïah u briew jong U Blei, ka da ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “To kren ha u Rehoboam u khun u Solomon, u syiem ka Judah, bad ha ki Israel baroh kiba ha Judah bad ha Benjamin, da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, Phin ym leit kiew, lymne ïaleh thma ïa la ki para: leit phai noh man la u briew sha la ïing: namar kane ka long na nga.’ ” Kumta, ki la shahshkor ïa ki ktien U Trai, bad ki la phai noh na kaba leit ïaleh ïa u Jeroboam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Rehoboam u la shong ha Jerusalem, bad u la tei ïa ki shnong jingïada ha Judah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la tei ïa ka Bethlehem keiñ, bad ka Etam, bad ka Tekoa,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ïa ka Beth-sur, bad ka Soko, bad ka Adullam,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ka Gath, bad ka Mareshah, bad ka Siph,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ka Adoraim, bad ka Lakhish, bad ka Asekah,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ka Sorah, bad ka Aijalon, bad ka Hebron, kiba ha Judah bad ha Benjamin, ki shnong ba la ker kut.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la tei pynskhem ïa ki kut, bad u la buh ki kaptan ha ki, bad ka jingkynshew jingbam, bad ka umphniang bad ka Waiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ha kawei kawei ka shnong u la buh ki stieh bad ki sum, bad u la pynskhem bha eh ïa ki. Te ka Judah bad ka Benjamin ki la dei ha u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi kiba la long ha Israel baroh, ki la ïawan sha u na ki phang jong ki baroh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Naba ki Lebi ki la iehnoh ïa la ki rudnong bad ïa kata kaba ki don, bad ki la wan sha Judah bad Jerusalem: naba u Jeroboam bad ki khun jong u, ki la kyntait noh ïa ki, ba kin ym ïoh trei ïa ka kam lyngdoh ha U Trai:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u la thung ïa u, ki lyngdoh ïa ki jaka bajrong, bad ïa ki 'lang sohmoh, bad ïa kita ki khun masi kiba u la thaw.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad hadien jong ki, kat kiba thmu ha la ka dohnud ban wad ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, na ki jaid Israel baroh, ki la wan sha Jerusalem ban kñia ha U Trai, U Blei jong ki kpa jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, ki la ai bor ïa ka hima Judah, bad ki la pynkhlaiñ ïa u Rehoboam u khun u Solomon, lai snem: namar ki la ïaid lai snem ha ka lynti u Dabid bad u Solomon.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Rehoboam u la ïoh tnga ïa ka Mahalath ka khun u Jerimoth u khun u Dabid, bad ïa ka Abihail ka khun u Eliab u khun u Jesse;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ka la kha khun shynrang ïa u; u Jeush, bad u Shemariah, bad u Saham.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad hadien jong ka u la shim ïa ka Maakah ka khun u Absalom; te ka la kha ha u ïa u Abijah, bad u Attai, bad u Sisa, bad u Shelomith.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Rehoboam u la ieit ïa ka Maakah ka khun u Absalom nalor ki tnga bad ki tnga kliar jong u baroh: (naba u la ïoh khatphra ngut ki tnga, bad hynriewphew ngut ki tnga kliar, bad u la pynkha arphew phra ngut ki khun shynrang bad hynriewphew ngut ki khun kynthei.)",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Rehoboam u la thung rangbah ïa u Abijah u khun ka Maakah, u nongsynshar keiñ hapdeng ki para jong u: naba u la thew ban pynlong syiem ïa u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la leh sian, bad u la pynsaphred ïa la ki khun shynrang baroh ha ki khyndew Judah bad Benjamin baroh, sha ka shnong ba la ker kut baroh: bad u la ai kyrhai ka jingbam ïa ki. Bad u la wad ki tnga shibun ïa ki."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba la pynskhem ïa ka hima u Rehoboam, bad ba u la khlaiñ, u la lyndet noh ïa ka hukum jong U Trai, bad ki Israel baroh lem bad u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ha ka snem ka basan jong u syiem Rehoboam, u Shishak u syiem ka Ijipt u la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka Jerusalem, namar ba ki la leh palat ïa U Trai,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad khat-ar spah ki kali, bad hynriewphew hajar ki nongshong kulai: bad uta u paidbah uba la wan lem bad u na ri Ijipt u bym lah ñiew shuh; ki Lubi, ki Sukki, bad ki nong Ethiopia.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la jop ïa ki shnong ba la ker kynroh kiba dei ha Judah, bad u la wan ha Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Shemaïah u nongïathuhlypa u la wan ha u Rehoboam, bad ha ki rangbah Judah, kiba la ïalum lang ha Jerusalem namar u Shishak, bad u la ong ha ki, “Kumne u ong U Trai, Phi la kyntait ïa nga, namar kata, nga la iehnoh ïa phi ha ka kti u Shishak.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, ki rangbah Israel bad u syiem ki la pynrit ïa lade; bad ki la ong, “U Trai u long u bahok.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba U Trai u la ïohi ba ki la pynrit ïa lade, ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Shemaïah, ka da ong, “Ki la pynrit ïa lade; ngan ym pynjot ïa ki: hynrei, ngan ai ïa ki, khyndiat ka jingïohlait, bad yn ym theh noh ïa ka jingbitar jong nga halor ka Jerusalem da ka kti u Shishak.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> La kumta ruh, kin long ki shakri jong u; ba kin ïoh tip ïa ka jingshakri jong nga, bad ïa ka jingshakri ki hima jong ki ri.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta u Shishak u syiem ka Ijipt u la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka Jerusalem, bad u la shim noh ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai, bad ki jingkynshew ka ïing u syiem; u la shim noh baroh phar: bad u la shim ruh ïa ki stieh ksiar kiba u Solomon u la thaw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ha ka jaka jong ki, u syiem Rehoboam u la thaw ki stieh rnong, bad u la aiti ïa ki ha ka kti ki kaptan ka karod, kiba ju ap ïa ka jingkhang ka ïing u syiem.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba u syiem u rung ha ka ïing U Trai, ki karod ki la ju wan rah ïa ki, bad ki la ju wallam pat ïa ki sha ka kamra ki karod.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad haba u la pynrit ïa lade, ka jingbitar U Trai ka la phai noh na u, ba un ym pynjot noh khoit ïa u: bad ha Judah la shem ruh ïa kiei kiei ki babha.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, u syiem Rehoboam u la pynskhem ïa lade ha Jerusalem, bad u la synshar: namar u Rehoboam u la sawphew wei snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar, bad u la synshar khathynñiew snem ha Jerusalem, ka shnong kaba U Trai u la jied na ki jaid Israel baroh, ban buh la ka kyrteng hangta: te ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka long “ka Naamah” ka nong Ammon.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew, naba um shym thew la ka dohnud ban wad ïa U Trai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki kam u Rehoboam, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, hato ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ki Jingïathuh u Shemaïah u nongïathuhlypa bad ki jong u Iddo u nongïohi, ha ka rukom ka jinghiar pateng? Bad la don ki jingïaleh thma borabor hapdeng u Rehoboam bad u Jeroboam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Rehoboam u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid: bad u Abijah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka bakhatphra snem u syiem Jeroboam, u Abijah u la sdang ban synshar halor ki Judah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la synshar lai snem ha Jerusalem: te ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Mikaïah” ka khun u Uriel na Gibeah. Te la don ka thma hapdeng u Abijah bad u Jeroboam.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Abijah u la leit ïaleh thma da u paidïapom ki rangbah bashlur, jin sawspah hajar ki rangbah ba la kynsai: bad u Jeroboam u la pynkhreh ïa ka thma ban ïaleh ïa u, da phraspah hajar ki rangbah ba la kynsai, kiba long ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Abijah u la ïeng halor u lum Semaraim, uba ha ka ri lum Ephraim, bad u la ong, “Ko Jeroboam bad ki Israel baroh, to sngew ïa nga;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> kam la dei ïa phi ban tip ba U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u la ai ïa ka hima Israel ha u Dabid ha la ka rta, ha u keiñ, bad ha ki khun jong u ruh da ka jutang ka mluh?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, pynban, u Jeroboam u khun u Nebat, u shakri u Solomon u khun u Dabid, u la ïeng joit, bad u la ïaleh pyrshah ïa la u kynrad.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad la ïalum ha u ki 'riewthala, ki khun u Belial keiñ, kiba la pyneh ïa lade ban ïaleh ïa u Rehoboam u khun u Solomon, mynba u Rehoboam u dang khynnah bad jemnud, te um lah ban ïaleh ïa ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Hynrei, mynta, phi mut ban ïaleh ïa ka hima U Trai ha ka kti ki khun u Dabid; bad phi long u paidbah byllien, bad phi don ryngkat bad phi ruh ki khun masi ksiar ïa kiba u Jeroboam u la thaw ha phi ban long ki blei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Phi la beh noh ne em ïa ki lyngdoh U Trai, ki khun u Aaron, bad ïa ki Lebi ruh de, bad phi la thung lyngdoh ïa lade katba kum ka rukom ki kynja bynriew ha kiwei pat ki ri? kumta ba uno uno u ban shu wan pynkyntang ïa lade da u masi lyngraw bad da ki hynñiew ki langbrot shynrang, uta keiñ, u lah ban long lyngdoh jong kita ki bymlong ki blei satia.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, shaphang jong ngi, U Trai u long U Blei jong ngi, bad ngim shym la kyntait ïa u; bad ngi don ruh ki lyngdoh kiba shakri ha U Trai, ki khun u Aaron keiñ, bad ki Lebi ruh de ha la ki kam:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ki thang ïa ki jingainguh thang bad ïa ka jingiw baiwbih ha U Trai man ka step bad man ka janmiet: ki buh ryntih ruh ïa ki 'pu pyni halor ka miej bakhuid; bad ïa ka dieng pynïeng sharak ksiar lem bad ki sharak jong ka, ban thang man ka janmiet: namar ma ngi, ngi rakhe ïa ka jingsumar U Trai U Blei jong ngi; hynrei, phi, phi la kyntait noh ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ha khmih, U Blei hi u long ryngkat bad ngi, ban ïalam ïa ngi, bad ki lyngdoh jong u ruh lem bad ki turoi ka jingmaham ban put ka jingmaham pyrshah ïa phi. A phi ki khun Israel, wat ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong phi; namar phin ym lah.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, u Jeroboam u la phah ki nongap thap ban wan tawiar na shadien jong ki: kumta, ki, ki la long na shakhmat ki Judah, bad kita ki nongap thap ki la long na shadien jong ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba ki Judah ki la kyrtiang, ha khmih, ka thma ka la long na shakhmat bad na shadien jong ki: te ki la pyrta ha U Trai, bad ki lyngdoh ruh ki la put ïa ki turoi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Judah ki la risa: te katba ki Judah ki la risa, la jia ba U Blei u la shoh ïa u Jeroboam bad ïa ki Israel baroh ha khmat u Abijah bad ki Judah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki khun Israel te ki la phet ïap na khmat ki Judah: bad U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Abijah bad ki briew jong u ki la pynïap ïa ki, da ka jingpynïap bakhraw: kumta, la pynkyllon ïap na ki Israel sanspah hajar ki rangbah ba la kynsai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumne keiñ, la pynhapoh ïa ki khun Israel ha kata ka por, bad ki khun Judah ki la jop, namar ba ki la shaniah ha U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Abijah te u la beh nadien u Jeroboam, bad u la knieh na u ïa ki nongbah, ïa ka Bethel bad ki shnong jong ka, bad ïa ka Jeshanah bad ki shnong jong ka, bad ïa ka Ephron bad ki shnong jong ka de.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Jeroboam um shym la ïoh bor shuh ha ki sngi u Abijah: bad U Trai u la shoh ïa u, bad u la ïap noh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, u Abijah u la nang khraw bor, bad u la shim khatsaw ngut ki tnga, bad u la pynkha arphew ar ngut ki khun shynrang, bad khathynriew ngut ki khun kynthei.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te kita kiwei ki kam u Abijah bad ki lynti jong u, bad ki jingong jong u ruh, la thoh keiñ ïa ki ha Ka Kot Batai u Iddo u nongïathuhlypa."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kumta, u Abijah u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid, bad u Asa u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u: ha ki sngi jong u, ka ri ka la suk shiphew snem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Asa u la leh ïa kata ka babha bad kaba dei ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong u:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> namar u la pynduh noh ïa ki duwan bakhyllah, bad ïa ki jaka bajrong, bad u la pynkyllon ïa ki mawbynna, bad u la khet noh ïa ki Asherah;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad u la hukum ïa ki Judah ban wad ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki, bad ban leh ïa ka aiñ bad ïa ka hukum de.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la pynduh noh ruh na ki shnong Judah baroh ïa ki jaka bajrong bad ïa ki durblei sngi: bad ka hima ka la suk ha khmat jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la tei ïa ki shnong ba la ker kynroh ha Judah: naba ka ri ka la suk, bad ba um don thma ha kito ki snem; namar U Trai u la ai ïa u ka jingshongthait.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar u la ong ha ki Judah, “To ngin ïatei ïa kine ki shnong, bad ngi ïatei ki kynroh baroh sawdong ïa ki, bad ïa ki kut, ïa ki khyrdop, bad ïa ki narkhang ruh de; ka ri ka dang don ha khmat jong ngi, namar ba ngi la wad ïa U Trai U Blei jong ngi; ngi la wad ïa u, te u la ai ka jingshongthait ïa ngi na baroh sawdong.” Kumta, ki la tei bad ki la man bha.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Asa u la don ki shipai rah stieh rah sum, na ki Judah laispah hajar; bad na ki Benjamin, kiba rah stieh bad kiba siat ryntieh, arspah phraphew hajar: kine baroh ki la long ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Serah u nong Ethiopia bad u paidïapom shi hajar hajar, bad ki kali ïapom laispah, u la wan ïaleh ïa ki; bad u la wan haduh Mareshah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Asa u la leit ban ïashem ïa u, bad ki la khreh riang ïa ka thma ha ka them Sephathah ha Mareshah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Asa u la khot kyrpad ha U Trai U Blei jong u, bad u la ong, “A Trai, ym don shuh nalor jong me u ban ïarap, hapdeng u badonbor bad u bymdonbor: to ïarap ïa ngi, A Trai U Blei jong ngi; namar ngi shaniah ha me, bad ha ka kyrteng jong me ngi wan ïaleh ïa une u paidbah. A Trai, me long U Blei jong ngi; wat ai ïa u briew ban jop ïa me.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, U Trai u la shoh jop ïa ki Ethiopia ha khmat u Asa, bad ha khmat ki Judah; te ki Ethiopia ki la phet ïap noh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Asa bad ki briew kiba la don bad u ki la beh ïa ki haduh Gerar: bad ki la kyllon ïap na ki Ethiopia katta haduh ba kim lah shuh ban pynbeit ïa lade; namar la pynjot noh ïa ki ha khmat U Trai, bad ha khmat u paidbah jong u; bad ki la kit noh shibun ka jinglute.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la pom ïa kita ki shnong baroh sawdong ïa ka Gerar; namar ka jingsheptieng ïa U Trai ka la ngat ha ki: bad ki la lute ïa kita ki shnong baroh; namar la don shibun bah ka jinglute ha ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la pom ïa ki ïing dara jong ki jingri, bad ki la ñiah noh kyrhai ki langbrot bad ki ut, bad ki la leit phai noh sha Jerusalem."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Mynsiem U Blei u la wan ha u Asaraïah u khun u Oded:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la leit mih noh ban tan ïa u Asa, bad u la ong ha u, “Ko Asa, bad phi baroh ki Judah bad ki Benjamin, to sngew ïa nga: U Trai u long ryngkat bad phi, katba phi long ryngkat bad u; bad lada phin wad ïa u, phin shem ïa u; hynrei, lada phin kyntait ïa u, u ruh un kyntait ïa phi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Mynta la slem bah ki Israel ki la long khlem U Blei bashisha, bad khlem u lyngdoh uba hikai, bad khlem ka hukum ruh:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> hynrei, haba ha ka jingshitom jong ki, ki la phai ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, bad ki la wad ïa u, ki la shem ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ha kito ki por ym don jingsuk satia ïa uta uba mih shabar, lymne ïa uta uba rung hapoh, hynrei, ki jingshitom bakhraw ki la don ha kiba shong ha ki ri baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad la pynlwet jin ïa ki, ka jaid bynriew ka ïaleh ïa ka jaid bynriew, bad ka shnong ka ïaleh ïa ka shnong: namar U Blei u la pynshitom ïa ki da ka jingjynjar baroh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, ma phi, to long khlaiñ, bad to wat pynjem ïa la ki kti: naba yn ai bainong ïa ka kam jong phi.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te haba u Asa u la ïohsngew ïa kine ki ktien, bad ïa ka jingïathuhlypa u Oded u nongïathuhlypa, u la sngewshlur, bad u la pynduh noh ïa kita ki jingijli na ka ri Judah bad Benjamin baroh, bad na ki shnong kiba u la knieh na ka ri lum Ephraim; bad u la pynthymmai ïa ka duwan U Trai, kaba don ha khmat ka batsha U Trai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la ïalum lang ïa ki Judah bad ki Benjamin baroh, bad ïa kita kiba shong ryngkat bad ki na Ephraim bad na Manasseh, bad na Simeon ruh: namar shibun bah na ki Israel ki la wanhap ha u, haba ki la ïohi ba Trai U Blei jong u, U don ryngkat bad u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, ki la ïalum lang ha Jerusalem ha u bnai u balai, ha ka bakhatsan snem ka jingsynshar u Asa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la kñia ha U Trai ha kata ka sngi, na kata ka jinglute kaba ki la wallam, hynñiewspah ki masi dab bad hynñiew hajar ki langbrot.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la ïathaw jutang ban wad ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki, da ka dohnud jong ki baroh bad da ka mynsiem jong ki baroh;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ba jar u ban ym wad ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, yn pynïap noh ïa u, la uba rit ne uba khraw, la u shynrang ne ka kynthei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la smai ha U Trai da ka ktien bajam, bad da ka jingrisa, bad da ki ronsing, bad ki bikur de.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki Judah baroh ki la kmen ha kata ka jingsmai: naba ki la smai da ka dohnud jong ki baroh, bad ki la wad ïa u da ka jingkwah jong ki baroh bad ki la shem ïa u: bad U Trai u la ai ka jingsuk ïa ki sawdong kylleng.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ïa ka Maakah ruh ka kmie u syiem Asa, u la beh noh na kaba long syiem, namar ba ka la thaw ka dur ba-ijli ïa ka Asherah; bad u Asa u la khet noh ïa ka dur jong ka, bad u la pynlwet ïa ka, bad u la thang ïa ka ha ka wah Kidron.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, ïa kita ki jaka bajrong ym shym la pynduh noh na Israel: la kumta ka dohnud u Asa ka la long kaba beit ha ki sngi jong u baroh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u la wallam sha ka ïing U Blei ïa kiei kiei kiba u kpa jong u, u la pynkyntang, bad ïa kiba u hi ruh u la pynkyntang, ïa ka rupa, bad ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang ruh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ym shym la don thma shuh haduh ka balaiphew san snem ka jingsynshar u Asa."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha ka balaiphew hynriew snem ka jingsynshar u Asa, u Baasha u syiem ki Israel u la leit kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka Judah, bad u la tei ïa ka Ramah, ba u lah ban ym shah ïano ïano ban leit mih ne ban wan sha u Asa u syiem ka Judah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u Asa u la sei noh ïa ka rupa bad ïa ka ksiar na ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai bad ki jong ka ïing u syiem, bad u la phah sha u Benhadad u syiem ka Syria, uba shong ha Damaskos, u da ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Ka don ka jingïateh jutang bad nga bad me, kumba ka la don hapdeng u kpa jong nga bad jong me: ha khmih, mynta nga la phah ka rupa bad ka ksiar sha me: khie leit, pynkheiñ ïa la ka jutang bad u Baasha u syiem ki Israel, ba un kynriah noh na nga.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Benhadad u la shahshkor ïa u syiem Asa, bad u la phah ïa ki kaptan ki paidïapom jong u ban ïaleh ïa ki shnong Israel; te ki la pom ïa ka Ijon, bad ïa ka Dan, bad ïa ka Abelmaim, bad ïa ki shnong jingkynshew jong ka Naphtali ruh de.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba u Baasha u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la iehnoh kaba tei ïa ka Ramah, bad u la pynpep noh ïa la ka jingtrei jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem Asa u la shim ïa ki Judah baroh; bad ki la kit noh ïa ki maw na Ramah, bad ïa ki dieng jong ka, da kiba u Baasha u la tei; bad u la tei ruh da kita ïa ka Geba bad ïa ka Mispah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ha kata ka por, u Hanani u nongïohi u la wan ha u Asa u syiem ka Judah, bad u la ong ha u, “Namar ba me la shaniah ha u syiem ka Syria, bad mem shym la shaniah ha U Trai U Blei jong me, namar kata keiñ, u paidïapom u syiem ka Syria u la lait noh na ka kti jong me.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hato ki Ethiopia bad ki Lub kim shym la long u paidbah bakhraw, bad ki kali ïapom bad ki nongshong kulai shibun eh? la kumta ruh, namar ba me la shaniah ha U Trai, U la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong me.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar ki khmat jong U Trai ki shad kylleng ha ka pyrthei baroh, ban pynkhlaiñ ïa lade bad kita kiba ka dohnud jong ki ka janai ha u. Ha kane, me la leh bieit; namar naduh mynta men sa ïoh ki thma.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u Asa u la bitar ïa uta u nongïohi, bad u la buh ïa u ha ka ïing byndi; namar u la sngewbitar lep ïa u namar kane. Bad u Asa u la ban bor ïa katto katne na ki briew ha kata ka por.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ha khmih, ki kam u Asa, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Judah bad Israel.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ha ka balaiphew khyndai snem ka jingsynshar jong u, u Asa u la pang na ki kjat; ka jingpang jong u ruh ka la jur shibun eh: pynban, ha la ka jingpang jong u um shym la wad ïa U Trai, hynrei, ïa ki nongpynkhiah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Asa u la thiah noh bad la ki kpa, bad u la ïap ha ka basawphew wei snem ka jingsynshar jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la tep ïa u ha ki jingtep jong u hi, kiba u la tih lypa ïa lade ha ka shnong u Dabid, bad ki la pynthiah ïa u ha ka jingthiah kaba la dap da ki jingiw baiwbih bad da ki masla ba bun jaid, kiba la khreh da ka buit stad ki Apothekari: bad ki la pynlong ka jingthang bakhraw ïa u."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u, bad u la pynkhlaiñ ïa lade pyrshah ïa ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la buh shipai ha ki nongbah ba la ker kut ka Judah baroh, bad u la buh ki karod ha ka ri Judah, bad ha ki shnong Ephraim, ïa kiba u Asa u kpa jong u, u la lah knieh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad U Trai u la long ryngkat bad u Jehoshaphat, namar ba u la ïaid ha ki lynti ki banyngkong u Dabid u kpa jong u, bad um shym la wad sha ki Baal;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> hynrei, u la wad sha U Blei u kpa jong u, bad u la ïaid ha ki hukum jong U, te ym ha ki jingleh ki Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, U Trai u la pynskhem ïa ka hima ha ka kti jong u: bad ka Judah baroh ka la wallam ki jingai sngewbha ha u Jehoshaphat; bad u la don spah bad ka burom kyrhai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad la pynkyntiew ïa ka dohnud jong u ha ki lynti U Trai: bad nalor kata, u la pynduh ïa ki jaka bajrong bad ïa ki Asherah na Judah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ha ka snem balai ka jingsynshar jong u, u la phah ruh ïa ki rangbah jong u, ïa u Ben-hail, bad u Obadaïah, bad u Sekharaïah, bad u Nathanil, bad u Mikaïah, ban hikai ha ki nongbah ka Judah;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ryngkat bad ki, ïa ki Lebi, ïa u Shemaïah keiñ, bad u Nethaniah, bad u Sebadiah, bad u Asahel, bad u Shemiramoth, bad u Jehonathan, bad u Adonijah, bad u Tobijah, bad u Tob-adonijah, ki Lebi; bad u Elishama bad u Jehoram ki lyngdoh, ryngkat bad ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki la hikai ha Judah, ki da don Ka Kitab Ka Hukum U Trai ryngkat bad ki; bad ki ïaid kylleng ïa ki nongbah ka Judah baroh, bad ki la hikai hapdeng ki briew.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka jingsheptieng U Trai ka la hap ha baroh ki hima ki ri kiba baroh sawdong ka Judah, kumta, kim shym ïaleh thma ïa u Jehoshaphat.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad na ki Philistia don kiba la wallam jingai sngewbha ïa u Jehoshaphat, bad ka rupa kum ka khrong; ki Arab ruh ki la wallam ki blang ïa u, hynñiew hajar hynñiewspah ki langbrot shynrang, bad hynñiew hajar hynñiewspah ki 'lang sohmoh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la nang khraw bor shikatdei eh; bad u la tei ïa ki ïing kut bad ki nongbah jingkynshew ha Judah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la don bun ki jingtrei ha ki nongbah ka Judah; bad ki nongïapom, ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur, ha Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kane ka long ka jingkheiñ jong ki katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki: na ki Judah, ki rangbah ki shi hajar: u Adnah u rangbah, bad ryngkat bad u, laispah hajar ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad uba bud ha u, u Jehohanan u rangbah, bad arspah phraphew hajar kiba bad u;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad uba bud ha u Amasaïah u khun u Sikhri, uba la aiti sngewbha ïa lade ha U Trai; bad ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur kiba bad u, arspah hajar;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad na ki Benjamin: u Eliada u riewkhlaiñ bashlur, bad arspah hajar kiba kieng ryntieh kieng stieh ryngkat bad u;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad uba bud ha u de u Jehosabad, bad shispah phraphew hajar kiba la khreh lypa ïa ka thma ryngkat bad u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kine ki long kita kiba ap ïa u syiem, nalor kita ïa kiba u syiem u la buh ha kita ki nongbah ba la ker kut ha ka Judah baroh."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Jehoshaphat u la don spah bad burom kyrhai; bad u la ïalok bad u Ahab.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ynda katto katne snem, u la leit hiar sha Samaria ha u Ahab. Bad u Ahab u la pynïap ki langbrot bad ki masi shibun eh na ka bynta jong u, bad na ka bynta ki briew kiba bad u, bad u la kyntu ïa u ban leit lem bad u sha Ramoth-gilead.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Ahab u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah, “Men leit ne em bad nga sha Ramoth-gilead?” U te u la ïathuh ha u, “Nga long kumba me long, bad ki briew jong nga kum ki briew jong me; bad ngin long lem bad me ha ka thma.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la ong ha u syiem ki Israel, “To ïakylli, nga kyrpad ïa me, na ka ktien U Trai mynta.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem ki Israel u la ïalum lang ïa ki nongïathuhlypa, sawspah ngut, bad u la ong ha ki, “Ngin leit sha Ramoth-gilead ban ïaleh thma, ne ngan pep?” Ki te ki la ong, “Khie leit; namar U Blei un ai noh ïa ka ha ka kti jong u syiem.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, u Jehoshaphat u la ong, “Hato ym don shuh ma u nongïathuhlypa U Trai, ba ngi lah ban ïakylli na u?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “Dang don sa uwei u briew da uba ngi lah ban kylli na U Trai: hynrei, nga isih ïa u; namar um ju ïathuhlypa ïa ka babha shaphang jong nga, hynrei, tang ïa ka basniew borabor: une u long u Mikaïah u khun u Imla.” Te u Jehoshaphat u la ong, “Wat ai ba u syiem un ong kumta.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem ki Israel u la khot ïa u ïunukh, bad u la ong, “Wallam kloi ïa u Mikaïah u khun u Imla.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel bad u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah ki la ïashong mar ha la ka khet, kiba la kup ïa la ki jaiñ syiem, bad ki la shong ha madan ha khmat ka khyrdop ka Samaria; bad ki nongïathuhlypa baroh ki ïathuhlypa ha khmat jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Sedekaïah u khun u Khenaanah u la thaw ïa lade ki reng nar, bad u la ong, “Kumne u ong U Trai, Da kine men tur ïa ka Syria, haduh ba kin da duh noh khoit.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki nongïathuhlypa baroh ki la ïathuhlypa kumta, ki ïa-ong, “Khie leit sha Ramoth-gilead, bad to jop; namar U Trai un ai noh ïa ka ha ka kti u syiem.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te uta u nonglam-ktien uba la leit khot ïa u Mikaïah u la kren ha u, u da ong, “Ha khmih, ki ktien ki nongïathuhlypa ki pyni ïa ka babha ïa u syiem da kawei ka shyntur: namar kata, nga kyrpad ïa me, to ka ktien jong me kan long kum kawei na ki jong ki, bad to kren bha ma me ruh.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Mikaïah u la ong, “Katba U Trai u im, ïa kaba U Blei jong nga u ong, ïa kata ngan kren.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad haba u la poi ha u syiem, u syiem u la ong ha u, “Ko Mikaïah, ngin leit sha Ramoth-gilead ban ïaleh thma, ne ngan pep?” U te u la ong, “Khie leit, bad to jop; bad yn ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong phi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u syiem u la ong ha u, “Katno sien ba ngan pynsmai ïa me ba men ym kren ei ei ha nga, hynrei, tang ïa kaba shisha ha ka kyrteng U Trai?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U te u la ong, “Nga la ïohi ïa ki Israel baroh ba ki la sakma halor ki lum, kum ki langbrot ki bymdon nongsharai: bad U Trai u la ong, ‘Kine kim don kynrad; to kin leit phai noh uwei uwei baroh sha la ïing ha kaba suk.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “Nga la ong ne em ïa me ba un ym ïathuhlypa ïa ka babha shaphang jong nga, hynrei, tang ïa ka basniew?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la ong, “Haba kumta, to sngew ïa ka ktien U Trai: Nga la ïohi ïa U Trai ba u shong halor ka khet jong u, bad u paidbah bneng baroh u ïeng sha ka kti kamon bad sha ka kti kadiang jong u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong, ‘Uei u ban riam ïa u Ahab u syiem ki Israel, ba un leit sha Ramoth-gilead bad ba un kyllon hangta?’ Bad uwei u kren da kumne, bad uwei u kren da kumtai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te la wan uwei u mynsiem, bad u la ïeng ha khmat U Trai, bad u la ong, ‘Ngan riam ma nga ïa u.’ Bad U Trai u la ong ha u, ‘Da kumno?’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u la ong, ‘Ngan leit mih, bad ngan long u mynsiem lamler ha ka shyntur ki nongïathuhlypa jong u baroh.’ Bad u la ong, ‘To men riam ma me ïa u, bad men lah ruh: khie leit, bad leh kumta.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar kata, ha khmih, U Trai u la buh ïa u mynsiem lamler ha ka shyntur kine ki nongïathuhlypa jong me; bad U Trai u la kren ïa ka basniew shaphang jong me.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, u Sedekaïah u khun u Khenaanah u la wan hajan, bad u la thab ïa u Mikaïah na ka ngab, bad u la ong, “Da kano ka lynti U Mynsiem U Trai u leit noh na nga ban kren ha me?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Mikaïah u la ong, “Ha khmih, men sa ïohi ha kata ka sngi, haba me leit rung ban rieh ïa lade ha ka kamra kaba kham shapoh.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la ong, “Shim phi ïa u Mikaïah, bad leit lam ïa u sha u Amon u rangbah ka shnong, bad sha u Joash u khun u syiem;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad to ong, ‘Kumne ong u syiem, “Set ïa une u briew ha phatok, bad bsa ïa u da u kpu ka jingshitom bad da ka um ka jingshitom, haduh ba ngan da wan phai pat ha kaba suk.” ’ ”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Mikaïah u la ong, “Lada men wan phai pat shisha ha kaba suk, U Trai um shym kren da nga.” U la ong ruh, “To sngew, phi ki paidbah baroh keiñ.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u syiem ki Israel bad u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah ki la leit sha Ramoth-gilead.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u syiem ki Israel u la ong ha u Jehoshaphat, “Nga ngan pynpher ïa lade, bad ngan leit sha ka thma; hynrei men phong ïa la ki jong ki jaiñ.” Kumta u syiem ki Israel u la pynpher ïa lade; te ki la leit sha ka thma.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u syiem ka Syria u la lah hukum ïa ki kaptan ki kali ïapom jong u, u ong, “Wat ïaleh ïa uba rit lane ïa uba khraw, hynrei, tang ïa u syiem ki Israel.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te haba ki kaptan ki kali ïapom ki la ïohi ïa u Jehoshaphat, ki la ong, “U dei u syiem ki Israel.” Namar kata, ki la phai noh ban ïaleh ïa u: hynrei, u Jehoshaphat u la pyrta jam, bad U Trai u la ïarap ïa u; bad U Blei u la pynkhih ïa ki ban leit noh na u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad haba ki kaptan ki kali ïapom ki la ïohi ba ym dei u syiem ki Israel, ki la phai noh na kaba beh ïa u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te uwei u briew u la wiat ïa la ka ryntieh kumba pda lymbneng, bad u la dei ïa u syiem ki Israel napdeng ki jingbteng ka jingphong nar: ynda kumta, u la ong ha u kashwan, “Pynphai ïa la ka kti, bad ïalam noh ïa nga na une u paidbah; namar nga la mynsaw jur.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ka thma ka la nang jur ha kata ka sngi: hynrei, u syiem ki Israel u shan ïa lade ha la ka kali ban ïaleh ïa ki Syria haduh janmiet; bad u la ïap hamar ba sep ka sngi."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah u la leit phai pat da kaba suk sha la ïing sha Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Jehu u khun u Hanani u nongïohi, u la leit tan ïa u, bad u la ong ha u syiem Jehoshaphat, “Hato me dei ban ïarap ïa ki bymman, bad ban ieit ïa kita kiba shun ïa U Trai? Namar kane, ka jingbitar na khmat U Trai ka don halor jong me.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> La kumta ruh, don kiei kiei ki babha ïa kiba la shem ha me, ha kaba me la pynduh noh ïa ki Asherah na ka ri, bad ba me la thew la ka dohnud ban wad ïa U Blei.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la shong ha Jerusalem: bad u la leit pat hapdeng u paidbah naduh Beer-sheba haduh ka ri lum Ephraim, bad u la wallam pat ïa ki sha U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la thung ki nongbishar ha ka ri ha ki nongbah ba la ker kynroh ka Judah, kawei pa kawei ka nongbah,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u la ong ïa ki nongbishar, “To pyrkhat ïa kaba phi leh: namar phim bishar na ka bynta u briew, hynrei, na ka bynta U Trai; bad u don lem bad phi ha kata ka jingbishar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata te, to ka jingsheptieng U Trai kan don ha phi; to sumar bha bad leh ïa ka: namar bad U Trai U Blei jong ngi ym don ka jingbymhok, lymne ka jingñiew shiliang khmat, lymne kaba bamsap.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nalor kata, u Jehoshaphat u la thung na ki Lebi bad ki lyngdoh, bad na ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa ki Israel, ha Jerusalem, na ka bynta ka jingbishar U Trai, bad na ka bynta ka jingïakajia. Te ki la leit phai sha Jerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “Kumne phin leh ha ka jingsheptieng ïa U Trai, da kaba shisha, bad da la ka dohnud ka bakhuid.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad lano lano haba wan ka jingïakajia ha phi na ki para jong phi kiba shong ha la ki nongbah, hapdeng ka snam bad ka snam, hapdeng ka aiñ bad ka hukum, ki hukum bad ki jingbishar, phin maham ïa ki, ba kin ym leh pop ïa U Trai, bad kumta ba ka jingbitar kan wan halor jong phi bad halor ki para jong phi: to leh ïa kane, te phin ym bit pop.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ha khmih, u Amariah u rangbah lyngdoh u long halor jong phi ha ki kam U Trai baroh; bad u Sebadiah u khun u Ishmael, u nongsynshar ka ïing Judah, ha ki kam u syiem baroh: ki Lebi ruh kin long ki rangbah ha khmat jong phi. Leh shlur, bad U Trai un long bad ki babha.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka la jia hadien kane, ba ki khun Moab, bad ki khun Ammon, bad ryngkat bad ki katto katne na ki nong Ammon, ki la wan ban ïaleh thma ïa u Jehoshaphat.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te don kiba la wan ïathuh ïa u Jehoshaphat, ki ïa-ong, “La wan u paidbah bakhraw, ban ïaleh ïa me na sha shiliang ka duriaw, na Syria keiñ; bad ha khmih, ki don ha Hasason-tamar” (kaba long “ka En-gedi”).",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la sheptieng, bad u la aiti ïa lade ban wad ïa U Trai; bad u la pynbna ka jingshah jingit ha ka Judah baroh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki Judah ki la ïalum lang, ban wad ka jingïarap na U Trai: na ki shnong Judah baroh keiñ ki la wan ban wad ïa U Trai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la ïeng ha ka jingïaseng lang ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem, ha ka ïing U Trai, ha khmat ka phyllaw bathymmai;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u la ong, “A Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ngi, me mem long U Blei ha bneng? Bad me mem long u nongsynshar halor ki hima ki jaid bynriew baroh? Bad ha ka kti jong me ka long ka bor bad ka jinglah, kumta ba ym don ba lah ban ïeng pyrshah ïa me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A U Blei jong ngi, me mem shym la beh noh ïa kiba ju shong ha kane ka ri ha khmat ki briew jong me ki Israel, bad me la ai ïa ka ha u symbai u Abraham u lok jong me ha la ka rta?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki la shong ha ka, bad ha ka ki la thaw ïa me ka jaka kyntang ïa ka kyrteng jong me, ki ïa-ong,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ‘Lada ka basniew ka wan ha ngi, ka waitlam, ka jingbishar, lane ka khlam, lane ka 'nemsniew, ngin ïeng ha khmat kane ka ïing, bad ha khmat jong me, (namar ka kyrteng jong me ka long ha kane ka ïing,) bad ngin pyrta ha me ha ka jingjynjar jong ngi, te men sngew bad men pynim.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te mynta, ha khmih, ki khun Ammon bad Moab bad lum Seir, ïa kiba mem shym la shah ïa ki Israel ban hiar thma ha ki, haba ki la wan na ri Ijipt, hynrei, ki la ïaid kiar noh ïa ki, bad kim shym la pynjot ïa ki;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ha khmih, kumno ki ai nong ïa ngi, ba ki wan beh noh ïa ngi na ka jingïoh kynti jong me, ïa kaba me la ai ha ngi ban ïoh pateng ïa ka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A U Blei jong ngi, hato men ym bishar ïa ki? namar ngim don bor ban ïaleh ïa une u paid bakhraw uba wan ban ïaleh ïa ngi; lymne ngim tip aïu ngin leh: hynrei, ki khmat jong ngi ki long ha me.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki Judah baroh ki la ïeng ha khmat U Trai, lem bad ki khun barit jong ki, ki tnga jong ki, bad ki khun jong ki de.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ha u Jahasiel u khun u Sekharaïah, u khun u Benaïah, u khun u Jeiel, u khun u Mattaniah, u kynja Lebi, na ki khun shynrang u Asaph, la wan U Mynsiem U Trai hapdeng ka jingïaseng lang;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u la ong, “To shahshkor, phi ki Judah baroh, bad phi kiba shong ha Jerusalem, bad me u syiem Jehoshaphat: kumne U ong U Trai ha phi, ‘Wat sheptieng, lymne wat khaw-eit namar une u paidbah bakhraw; namar ka thma kam long ka jong phi, hynrei, ka jong U Blei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Lashai to phin leit hiar ban ïaleh ïa ki: ha khmih, ki wan na ka thiep Sis; bad phin shem ïa ki ha ka bakut ka them, ha shuwa ka khlaw Jeruel.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Phim donkam ban ïaleh ha kane ka thma: to buh beit ïa lade, to ïeng thik, bad khmih ïa ka jingpynim U Trai bad phi, ko Judah bad Jerusalem:’ wat sheptieng, lymne khaw-eit: to khie leit lashai ban ïaleh ïa ki; namar U Trai u long lem bad phi.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la pyndem ïa la ka khlieh bad la ka khmat sha ka khyndew: bad ki Judah bad ki nong Jerusalem baroh ki la hap dem ha khmat U Trai, ki ïamane ïa U Trai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki Lebi, kiba na ki khun ki Kohath bad kiba na ki khun ki Korah, ki la ïeng joit ban ïaroh ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, da ka ktien bajam eh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki la khie dang step lashai, bad ki la leit mih sha ka khlaw Tekoa: te katba ki dang leit, u Jehoshaphat u la ïeng bad u la ong, “To sngew ïa nga, ko Judah, bad phi ki nong Jerusalem; to ngeit ha U Trai U Blei jong phi, kumta yn pynskhem ïa phi; to ngeit ïa ki nongïathuhlypa jong u, kumta, phin man bha.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad haba u la lah ïapyrkhat bad u paidbah, u la thung ïa kita ki ban rwai ha U Trai, bad ki ban ïaroh ïa ka jingitynnad ka jingkhuid, katba ki ïaïaid ha shuwa ki paidïapom, bad ba kin ong, “To ainguh ïa U Trai; namar ka jingisynei jong u ka neh junom.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te haba ki la sdang ban rwai bad ban ïaroh, U Trai u la buh ki nongap thap pyrshah ïa ki khun Ammon, Moab, bad Lum Seir, kiba la wan ban ïaleh ïa ka Judah; bad la jop ïa ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar ki khun Ammon bad Moab ki la ïeng ïaleh ïa kiba shong ha u lum Seir, ban pynïap bad ban pynduh noh khoit ïa ki: bad haba ki la dep ïa kiba shong ha u lum Seir, uwei uwei baroh u la ïarap ban ïa-pynïap paralok.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba ki Judah ki la wan sha ka kut ap phira ka ri khlaw, ki la khmih ha uta u paidbah; bad ha khmih, ki la long ki metïap ba la kyllon ha khyndew, bad ym don uwei ba la ïohlait.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad haba u Jehoshaphat bad ki briew jong u ki la wan ban shim ïa ka jinglute na ki, ki la shem hapdeng jong ki shibun ka spah bad ki metïap, bad ki jingdeng bakordor, ïa kiba ki la ïalaw noh na ka bynta ïa lade, tam ïa kaba ki lah ban kit: bad ki la long lai sngi ha kaba shim ïa ka jinglute, ka la long kaba bun katta katta.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ha ka sngi ka basaw ki la ïalum lang ha ka them Berakah; namar hangta ki la kyrkhu ïa U Trai; namar kata, ïa ka kyrteng kata ka jaka la khot “Ka Them Berakah”, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïaphai noh, u briew ka Judah bad Jerusalem baroh, bad u Jehoshaphat ha shuwa jong ki, ban leit pat sha Jerusalem da ka jingkmen; namar U Trai u la pynrisa ïa ki halor ki nongshun jong ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki la wan sha Jerusalem bad ki nebel bad ki duitara bad ki ronsing sha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ka jingsheptieng ïa U Trai ka la long ha baroh ki hima jong kita ki ri, haba ki la ïohsngew ba U Trai u la ïaleh ïa ki nongshun ki Israel.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta, ka hima u Jehoshaphat ka la long kaba suk: namar U Blei jong u, U la ai ïa u ka jingshongthait baroh sawdong.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la synshar halor ka Judah: u la long laiphew san snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar arphew san snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka long “ka Asubah” ka khun u Shilhi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u la ïaid ha ka lynti u Asa u kpa jong u, bad um shym la kynriah na ka, u da leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki jaka bajrong ym shym la pynduh noh; lymne ki paidbah kim pat shym la thew ïa la ki dohnud sha U Blei ki kpa jong ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jehoshaphat, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Jingïathuhkhana u Jehu u khun u Hanani, ïa kaba la buh ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Ki Israel.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad hadien kane, u Jehoshaphat u syiem ka Judah u la pynïasoh ïa lade bad u Ahasaïah u syiem ki Israel; uta uba la leh sniew eh:",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad u la ïasoh ïa lade bad u ban thaw lieng ban leit sha Tarshish: bad ki la thaw ïa kita ki lieng ha Esion-geber.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te u Elieser u khun u Dodabahu uba na Mareshah u la ïathuhlypa pyrshah ïa u Jehoshaphat, u da ong, “Namar ba me la pynïasoh ïa lade bad u Ahasaïah, U Trai u la pynjot noh ïa ki kam jong me.” Bad ki lieng ki la pait, ba kim lah ban leit sha Tarshish."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Jehoshaphat u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad la tep ïa u bad ki kpa jong u ha ka shnong u Dabid: bad u Jehoram u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la don ki para ki khun u Jehoshaphat, u Asariah, bad u Jehiel bad u Sekharaïah, bad u Asariah, bad u Mikhael, bad u Shephatiah: kine baroh ki la long ki khun u Jehoshaphat u Syiem ki Israel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u kpa jong ki, u la ai ki jingai shibun ïa ki, ïa ka rupa, bad ka ksiar, bad kiei kiei kiba kordor, lem bad ki shnong ba la ker kynroh ha Judah: hynrei, ïa ka hima u la ai ïa u Jehoram, namar u long u khun nyngkong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u Jehoram u la kiew khet halor ka hima u kpa jong u, bad ba u la pynkhlaiñ ïa lade, u la pynïap ïa ki para jong u baroh da ka waitlam, bad ïa bun ruh na ki bakhraw batri ki Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Jehoram u la long laiphew ar snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar phra snem ha Jerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la ïaid ha ka lynti ki syiem ki Israel, kumba la leh ka ïing u Ahab: namar u la ïoh tnga ïa ka khun kynthei u Ahab: bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, U Trai um mon ban pynjot noh ïa ka ïing u Dabid, namar kata ka jutang ba u la pynlong bad u Dabid, bad namar ba u la kular ban ai ka sharak ïa u bad ïa ki khun jong u borabor.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ha ki sngi jong u, ki Edom ki la ïaleh ban lait na ka kti ki Judah, bad ki la thung syiem halor jong ki hi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jehoram u la leit mih lem bad ki kaptan jong ki, bad ki kali ïapom jong u baroh lem bad u: bad u la ïeng mynmiet, bad u la pom ïa ki Edom kiba la ker tawiar ïa u baroh sawdong, bad ïa ki kaptan ki kali ïapom.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, ki Edom ki la ïaleh, ki la lait na ka kti ki Judah, haduh kane ka sngi: ynda kumta, ka Libnah ruh ka la ïaleh, ka la lait ha kajuh ka por na ka kti jong u: namar ba u la kyntait noh ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nalor kata, u la thaw ki jaka bajrong ha ki lum Judah, bad u la pynleh ïa kiba shong ha Jerusalem ban klim noh, bad u la ïalam bakla ïa ki Judah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te la wan ka jingthoh sha u na u Elijah u nongïathuhlypa, kaba ong, “Kumne U ong U Trai, U Blei u Dabid u kpa jong me, ‘Namar ba mem shym la ïaid ha ki lynti u Jehoshaphat u kpa jong me, lymne ha ki lynti u Asa u syiem ka Judah;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> hynrei, me la ïaid ha ka lynti ki syiem ki Israel, bad me la pynleh ïa ki Judah bad ïa kiba shong ha Jerusalem ban klim noh, kumba la leh ka ïing u Ahab; bad me la pynïap ruh ïa ki para jong me kiba na ïing u kpa jong me, kiba kham bha ban ïa me:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ha khmih, U Trai un shoh da ka khlam bajur ïa ki briew jong me, bad ïa ki khun jong me, bad ïa ki tnga jong me, bad ïa kaba me don baroh:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad men ïoh ka jingpang kaba jur da ka bapang ki snier jong me, haduh ba ki snier jong me kin mih noh namar kata ka jingpang, ha la ka sngi.’ ”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad U Trai u la pynkhih pyrshah ïa u Jehoram ïa ka mynsiem ki Philistia, bad ki Arab kiba hajan ki Ethiopia:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ki la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka Judah, bad ki la pei sha ka, bad ki la kit noh ïa ka spah baroh ïa kaba la shem ha ïingsyiem, bad ïa ki khun jong u ruh, bad ïa ki tnga jong u; kumta ba um don shuh u khun ba la ieh ïa u, sa tang u Jehoahas, u khun bakhatduh jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad hadien kane baroh, U Trai u la shoh ïa u ha ki snier jong u da ka jingpang ka bym lah pynkhiah shuh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka la jia te, ynda katto katne, ha ka bakut ar snem, ba ki snier jong u ki la mih noh namar kata ka jingpang jong u, bad u la ïap na ki jingpang bajur. Bad ki briew jong u kim shym pynlong ka jingthang na ka bynta jong u, kum ka jingthang ïa ki kpa jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U la long laiphew ar snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar, bad u la synshar ha Jerusalem phra snem: bad u la leit noh bymdon ba bynnud ïa u; bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid, hynrei, ym dei ha ki jingtep ki syiem."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ki Jerusalem ki la pynlong syiem ha ka jaka jong u ïa u Ahasaïah u khun bakhatduh jong u: namar uta u paid uba la wan lem bad ki Arab sha ka jaka shong dara u la pynïap noh ïa kiba san baroh. Kumta u Ahasaïah u khun u Jehoram u syiem ka Judah u la synshar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Ahasaïah u la long sawphew ar snem haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar shi snem ha Jerusalem; bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka long “ka Athaliah” ka khun u Omri.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U ruh u la ïaid ha ki lynti ka ïing u Ahab: namar ka kmie jong u ka long ka nongpyni buit ïa u ban leh bymman.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kumba la leh ka ïing u Ahab: namar ki la long ki nongpyni buit ïa u hadien ba la ïap u kpa jong u, ïa ka jingjot jong u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la ïaid ruh katba kum ka jingpynibuit jong ki, bad u la leit lem bad u Jehoram u khun u Ahab u syiem ki Israel ban ïaleh thma ïa u Hasael u syiem ka Syria ha Ramoth-gilead: bad ki Syria ki la pynmong ïa u Joram.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la phai ban ïoh khiah ha Jesril na kita ki jingmong ba ki la pynmong ïa u ha Ramah, haba u la ïaleh ïa u Hasael u syiem ka Syria. Bad u Asariah u khun u Jehoram u syiem ka Judah u la leit hiar ban khmih ïa u Jehoram u khun u Ahab ha Jesril, namar u la pang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka jingpynjot ïa u Ahasaïah ka la long na U Blei, ha kata kaba u leit sha u Joram: namar haba u la poi, u la leit mih lem bad u Jehoram ban ïaleh ïa u Jehu u khun u Nimshi, ïa uba U Trai u la thung ban ot noh ïa ka ïing u Ahab.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka la jia te, katba u Jehu u dang leh ïa ka jingbishar halor ka ïing u Ahab, ba u la shem ïa ki bakhraw batri ka Judah, bad ïa ki khun ki hynmen u Ahasaïah, kiba shakri ïa u Ahasaïah, bad u la pynïap ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la wad ïa u Ahasaïah, bad ki la kem ïa u, (naba u rieh ha Samaria), bad ki la leit lam ïa u sha u Jehu, bad ki la pynïap ïa u; bad ki la tep ïa u, namar ki la ong, “U long u khun u Jehoshaphat, uba la wad ïa U Trai da ka dohnud jong u baroh.” Te ka ïing u Ahasaïah kam don bor shuh ban bat ïa ka hima.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ka Athaliah ka kmie u Ahasaïah ka la ïohi ba u khun jong ka u la ïap, ka la ïeng bad ka la pynduh noh ïa ki khun syiem baroh na ka ïing Judah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, ka Jehoshabeath, ka khun u syiem, ka la shim ïa u Joash u khun u Ahasaïah, bad ka la tuh noh ïa u napdeng ki khun u syiem ïa kiba la pynïap noh, bad ka la buh ïa u bad ïa ka aïa jong u ha ka kamra thiah. Kumta, ka Jehoshabeath, ka khun u syiem Jehoram, ka tnga u Jehoïada u lyngdoh, (namar ka long ka para u Ahasaïah) ka la buhrieh ïa u na ka Athaliah, kumta ba kam shym la pynïap ïa u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la long lem bad kiba la buhrieh ha ka ïing U Blei hynriew snem bad ka Athaliah ka la synshar halor ka ri."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka snem ka bahynñiew u Jehoïada u la pynskhem ïa lade, bad u la shim ïa ki rangbah shispah, ïa u Asaraïah u khun u Jeroham, bad ïa u Ishmael u khun u Jehohanan, bad ïa u Asaraïah u khun u Obed, bad ïa u Maaseïah u khun u Adaïah, bad ïa u Elishaphat u khun u Sikhri, ban ïateh jutang bad u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki la ïaleit kylleng ka Judah, bad ki la ïalum ïa ki Lebi na ki nongbah baroh jong ka Judah, bad ïa ki rangbah jong ki ïing ki kpa jong ki Israel, bad ki la wan ha Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te uta u paidlang baroh ki la pynlong ïa ka jutang bad u syiem ha ka ïing U Blei. Bad u la ong ha ki, “Ha khmih, u khun u syiem un synshar, kumba U Trai u la kren shaphang ki khun u Dabid.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kane ka long kaba phi dei ban leh: shi bynta na ka balai jong phi, kiba wan hapoh ha ka sngi Sabbaton, na ki lyngdoh bad na ki Lebi, kin long ki nongap jingkhang;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad shi bynta kin long ha ka ïing u syiem; bad shi bynta ha ka khyrdop ka nongrim: bad u paidbah baroh un long ha ka phyllaw ka ïing U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, wat ai ïano ïano ruh ban wan hapoh ka ïing U Trai, tang ki lyngdoh hi, bad kita kiba shakri na ki Lebi; kin wan hapoh, naba ki long ki bakhuid: hynrei, u paidbah baroh kin ïasumar ïa ka jingap jong U Trai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki Lebi kin ïeng tawiar ïa u syiem, man la u briew lem bad ki atiar jong u ha la ka kti; bad jar uba wan hapoh ka ïing, to pynïap ïa u: bad to long phi bad u syiem haba u leit shapoh, bad haba u mih shabar.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, ki Lebi bad ki Judah baroh ki la leh baroh kat kumba u Jehoïada u lyngdoh u la hukum: bad ki la shim uwei uwei baroh ïa la ki briew jong u, kita kiba dei ban wan hapoh ha ka sngi Sabbaton, lem bad kita kiba dei ban mih shabar ha ka sngi Sabbaton; naba u Jehoïada u lyngdoh um shym pyllait ïa ki jingkylliang sngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jehoïada lyngdoh u la aiti ha ki rangbah shispah ïa ki sum, bad ïa ki 'tiehbah, bad ïa ki stieh, kiba la long ki jong u syiem Dabid, kiba la don ha ka ïing U Blei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la buh ïa u paidbah baroh, man la u briew bad la ka atiar ha ka kti jong u, naduh ka krung kamon jong ka ïing haduh ka krung kadiang jong ka ïing, ter ter najan ka duwan bad ka ïing, hajan u syiem baroh sawdong.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la pynmih ïa u khun u syiem, bad ki la pynphong ka pansngiat halor jong u, bad ki la ai ha u ïa kata ka jingphla, bad ki la thung syiem ïa u: bad u Jehoïada bad ki khun jong u ki la pynsleh ïa u; bad ki la ong, “U Blei un pynim ïa u syiem.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba ka Athaliah ka la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa jong u paidbah ba ki ïamareh bad ki ïaroh ïa u syiem, ka la wan sha u paidbah hapoh ka ïing U Trai:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ka la khmih, te ha khmih, u syiem u la ïeng hajan u rishot jong u ha ka phyllaw, bad ki kaptan bad ki turoi hajan u syiem; te ki paidbah ka ri baroh ka la ïalehkmen, bad ki la put turoi; ki nongrwai ruh ki la tem ki jingtem jingrwai, bad ki la ïalam ïa ka jingrwai ïaroh. Ynda kumta, ka Athaliah ka la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad ka la ong, “Ka jingshetkylla, ka jingshetkylla!”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Jehoïada u lyngdoh u la pynmih ïa ki rangbah shispah ïa kiba la thung halor u paidïapom, bad u la ong ha ki, “Pynmih noh ïa ka hapdeng ki jingker; bad ïa uta uba bud ïa ka, to pynïap ïa u da ka waitlam”: naba u lyngdoh u la ong, “Wat pynïap ïa ka hapoh ka ïing U Trai.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, ki la pyllait lynti ïa ka, te ka la leit sha ka phyllaw Ka Khyrdop Kulai sha ka ïing u syiem: bad ki la pynïap ïa ka hangta.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Jehoïada u la pynlong ïa ka jutang hapdeng jong u hi, bad u paidbah baroh, bad u syiem, ba ki dei ban long ki briew jong U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u paidbah baroh ki la leit sha ka ïing u Baal, bad ki la pynkyllon ïa ka, bad ki la lympat ïa ki duwan jong u bad ïa ki dur jong u lyngkhot lyngkhot, bad ki la pynïap ïa u Mattan u lyngdoh jong u Baal ha khmat ki duwan.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Jehoïada u la buh ïa ki kam jong ka ïing U Trai hapoh ka kti ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, ïa kiba u Dabid u la ïabynta ha ka ïing U Trai, ban ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang jong U Trai, kumba la thoh ha Ka Hukum u Moses, da kaba kmen bad kaba rwai, katba kum ka rukom u Dabid.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la buh ki nongap ha ki khyrdop ka ïing U Trai, ba uno uno u bymkhuid kumno kumno un ym ïoh rung hapoh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u la shim ïa ki rangbah shispah, bad ïa ki bakhraw batri, bad ïa ki nongsynshar jong u paidbah, bad ïa ki briew baroh jong kata ka ri, bad ki la wallam arsut ïa u syiem na ka ïing U Trai: bad ki la wan lyngba ka khyrdop ba haneng sha ka ïing u syiem, bad ki la buh ïa u syiem halor ka khet jong ka hima.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, ki briew ka ri baroh ki la ïalehkmen, bad kata ka shnong ka la suk: bad ki la pynïap ïa ka Athaliah da ka waitlam."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Joash u la hynñiew snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar sawphew snem ha Jerusalem: te ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Sibiah” kaba na Beer-sheba.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Joash u la leh ïa kaba dei ha khmat U Trai baroh ki sngi u Jehoïada lyngdoh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Jehoïada u la pynïoh ar ngut ki tnga ha u; bad u la pynkha ki khun shynrang bad ki khun kynthei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te hadien kane, u Joash u la thmu ban shna pat ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la lum lang ïa ki lyngdoh bad ïa ki Lebi, bad u la ong ha ki, “To khie leit sha ki nongbah Judah, bad to lum sbai na ki Israel baroh ban shna pat ïa ka ïing U Blei jong phi man la ka snem, bad to sumar ba phin pynkloi ïa ka kam.” Hynrei, ki Lebi kim shym la pynkloi ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u syiem u la khot ïa u Jehoïada u rangbah, bad u la ong ha u, “Balei mem shym la dawa na ki Lebi ba kin wallam na Judah bad na Jerusalem ïa kata ka khrong jong u Moses u shakri jong U Trai, bad na u paidlang Israel, na ka bynta ka ïingjaiñ ka jingphla?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naba ki khun ka Athaliah, kata ka kynthei bymman, ki la pynpra noh ïa ka ïing U Blei; bad ïa kiei kiei ba la kyntang jong ka ïing U Trai ki la ai noh ha ki Baal.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, u syiem u la hukum, te ki la thaw ka synduk, bad ki la buh ïa ka shabar ha ka khyrdop ka ïing U Trai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki la pynlong ka jingpynbna kylleng ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem, ban wallam na ka bynta U Trai ïa ka khrong ïa kaba u Moses u shakri U Blei u la buh halor ki Israel ha ka ri khlaw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki rangbah baroh bad u paidbah baroh ki la ïalehkmen, bad ki la ïawallam, bad ki la ïanoh hapoh kata ka synduk, haduh ba ki la lah dep.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ka la jia, ba ha kano ma ka por ba la wallam ïa kata ka synduk ha ka kamra thoh jong u syiem da ka kti ki Lebi, bad haba ki la ïohi ba la don bun sbai, u nongthoh u syiem bad u shakri u rangbah lyngdoh ki la wan bad ki la pynsuda ïa ka synduk, bad ki la shim ïa ka, bad ki la leit lam pat sha la ka jaka. Kumne ki la leh man la ka sngi, bad ki la lum sbai shibun eh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u syiem bad u Jehoïada ki la ai ïa ka ha kita kiba trei ïa ka kam ka ïing U Trai; bad ki la wer ïa ki nongtrei kynroh bad ïa ki misteri ban shna pat ïa ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa kita ruh kiba trei nar bad rnong ban shna ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, ki nongtrei ki la trei, bad ki la pynjanai ïa ka jingtrei, bad ki la pynïeng ïa ka ïing U Blei ha la ka jinglong, bad ki la pynskhem ïa ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba ki la lah dep, ki la wallam ïa ki sbai kiba sah ha khmat u syiem bad u Jehoïada, da kita la thaw ïa ki khiew ki pliang ïa ka ïing U Trai, ki khiew ki pliang keiñ ïa ka ban shakri, bad ban ainguh ruh, bad ki siang, bad ki pliang ksiar bad rupa. Te ki la ainguh ki jingainguh thang ha ka ïing U Trai borabor baroh ki sngi u Jehoïada.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, u Jehoïada u la tymmen bad u la dap ki sngi jong u, bad u la ïap; shispah laiphew snem ka rta u la long haba u la ïap.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki la tep ïa u ha ka nongbah u Dabid hapdeng ki syiem, namar ba u la leh bha ha Israel, bad sha U Blei bad ka ïing jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te hadien ba la ïap u Jehoïada, la wan ki rangbah Judah, bad ki la ïanguh ïa u syiem. Te u syiem u la shahshkor ïa ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki la kyntait ïa ka ïing U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki, bad ki la shakri ïa ki Asherah bad ïa ki bleithaw: te ka jingbitar ka la hap halor ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem namar kane ka jingbit pop jong ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Pynban, u la phah ki nongïathuhlypa ha ki, ban wallam pat ïa ki sha U Trai; bad ki la phla pyrshah ïa ki: hynrei, kim shym la shahshkor.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te U Mynsiem U Blei u la wan ha u Sekharaïah u khun u Jehoïada lyngdoh; te u la ïeng halor u paidbah, bad u la ong ha ki, “Kumne u ong U Blei, Balei phi ryngkang ïa ka hukum U Trai, ba phim lah ban man bha? Namar ba phi la kyntait ïa U Trai, u ruh u la kyntait ïa phi.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki la ïashet ïa u, bad ki la lynthem maw ïa u da ka hukum u syiem ha ka phyllaw ka ïing U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumne u Joash uba u syiem um shym la kynmaw ïa ka jinglehbha kaba u Jehoïada u kpa jong u, u la leh ha u, hynrei, u la pynïap ïa u khun jong u. Te haba u la ïap, u la ong, “U Trai un khmih ïa kane, bad un pan ïa ka.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ka la jia ha ka bakut jong kata ka snem, ba ki shipai jong ki Syria ki la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa u: bad ki la wan ha Judah bad Jerusalem, bad ki la pynduh ïa ki rangbah baroh jong u paidbah napdeng ki paidbah, bad ki la phah ïa ka jinglute baroh na ki sha u syiem ka Damaskos.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Naba ki shipai Syria ki la wan tang khyndiat ki briew; te U Trai u la ai noh ïa u paidïapom babun eh ha ka kti jong ki, namar ba ki la kyntait ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki. Kumta ki la leh ïa ka jingbishar halor u Joash.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba ki la leit noh na u, (naba ki la iehnoh ïa u ha ki jingpang bajur,) ki shakri jong u ki la ïashet ïa u na ka bynta ka snam ki khun u Jehoïada lyngdoh, bad ki la pynïap ïa u ha ka jingthiah jong u, te u la ïap; te ki la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid, hynrei, kim shym la tep ïa u ha ki jingtep jong ki syiem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kine te ki long kita kiba la ïashet ïa u; u Sabad u khun ka Shimeath ka nong Ammon, bad u Jehosabad u khun ka Shimrith ka nong Moab.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te shaphang ki khun jong u, bad shaphang ka jingkhraw ki jingkit ba la buh halor jong u, bad shaphang kaba tei pat ïa ka ïing U Blei, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kot Batai jong Ka Kitab Ki Syiem. Bad u Amasaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Amasaïah u la long arphew san snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar arphew khyndai snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Jehoaddan” kaba na Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, hynrei, ym da ka dohnud kaba sngur.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba la pynskhem ïa ka hima ha u, u la pynïap ïa kita ki shakri jong u kiba la pynïap ïa u syiem uba u kpa jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki khun jong ki um shym la pynïap, hynrei, u la leh kat kumba la thoh ha Ka Hukum ha Ka Kitab u Moses, kumba U Trai u la hukum, u da ong, “Ki kpa kin ym ïap na ka bynta ki khun, lymne ki khun kin ym ïap na ka bynta ki kpa; hynrei, u briew baroh un ïap na ka bynta la ka jong hi ka pop.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Amasaïah u la ïalum lang ruh ïa ki Judah, bad u la buh ryntih ïa ki katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, hapoh ki rangbah shihajar bad ki rangbah shispah, ïa ki Judah bad ki Benjamin baroh keiñ: bad u la ñiew ïa ki naduh kiba arphew snem bad kiba tam, bad u la shem laispah hajar ki rangbah ba la kynsai, kiba la bit ban hiar thma, kiba la lah ban bat sum bat stieh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la wai ruh shispah talent rupa ïa shispah hajar ngut ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur na ki Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, la wan u briew jong U Blei ha u, u da ong, “Ko syiem, wat shah ba ki shipai Israel kin leit ryngkat bad me: naba U Trai um long ryngkat bad ki Israel, bad ki khun u Ephraim baroh keiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, lada men leit, to leh shlur to long khlaiñ ban ïaleh thma: U Blei un pynkyllon ïa me ha khmat u nongshun; naba U Blei u donbor ban ïarap, bad ban pynkyllon.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Amasaïah u la ong ha uta u briew jong U Blei, “Hynrei, ngin leh kumno ïa kita ki shispah talent kiba ngi la ai ha ki shipai Israel?” Te uta u briew jong U Blei u la ïathuh, “U Trai u lah ban ai ïa me kham bun eh ban ïa kane.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u Amasaïah u la pynkhlad noh ïa ki, ïa ki shipai kiba la wan sha u na Ephraim keiñ, ba kin leit phai noh sha la shnong: namar kata, ka jingbitar jong ki ka la meh lep ïa ki Judah, bad ki la leit phai sha la shnong ha ka jingbitar bakhraw.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Amasaïah u la leh shlur, bad u la ïalam ïa la u paidbah, u la leit ruh sha ka Them Mluh, bad u la pom shiphew hajar na ki khun Seir.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ïa kiwei pat ki shiphew hajar ki khun u Judah ki la kem im, bad ki la wallam sha khlieh uwei u mawsiang, bad ki la pynnoh ïa ki na khlieh uta u mawsiang, ba la pynlwet jin ïa ki baroh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ki shipai jong kata ka kynhun kaba u Amasaïah u la pynphai noh, ba kin ym leit bad u sha ka thma, ki la hiar ha ki nongbah ka Judah, naduh Samaria haduh Beth-horon, bad ki la pom lai hajar na ki, bad ki la knieh shibun ka jinglute.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te hadien ba u Amasaïah u la wan phai na kaba pynïap ïa ki nong Edom, u la wallam ïa ki blei jong ki khun Seir, bad u la pynïeng ïa ki ban long ki blei jong u, bad u la dem ha khmat jong ki, bad u la thang jingiwbih ha ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Namar kata, ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep ïa u Amasaïah, bad u la phah ïa u nongïathuhlypa sha u, uba la ong ha u, “Balei ba me la leit wad ïa ki blei jong kita ki briew, ki bym shym la pyllait ïa la ki briew na ka kti jong me?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te katba u dang kren bad u, u syiem u la ong ha u, “Hato ngi la thung ïa me na ka jingsylla jong u syiem? Sngap jar; balei yn shoh ïap ïa me?” Ynda kumta, u nongïathuhlypa u la sngap, bad u la shu ong, “Nga tip ba U Blei u la thmu ban pynjot ïa me, namar me la leh ïa kane, bad mem shym la shahshkor ïa ka jingpyni jong nga.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah u la ïasylla, bad u la phah sha u Joash, u khun u Jehoahas u khun u Jehu u syiem ki Israel, u da ong, “Ïa, ngin thaw ïakhmih kai markhmat.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Joash u syiem ki Israel u la phah sha u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah, u da ong, “U dieng shiah uba ha Lebanon u la phah ha u dieng Kedar uba ha Lebanon, u da ong, ‘To buh kurim ïa ka khun jong me ha u khun jong nga’: te uwei u mrad khlaw uba ha Lebanon u la ïaid nangta, bad u la ïuh roit ïa uta u dieng shiah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Me ong, ‘Ha khmih, me la jop ïa ka Edom’; bad ka dohnud jong me ka la pynsngew meng ïa me ban sngewsarong: to sah ha la shnong; balei men lushia ban sniew ïa lade, ba men kyllon, ma me hi, bad ka Judah ruh lem bad me?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, u Amasaïah um sngap satia; naba ka la long na U Blei, ba un ïoh ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki nongshun jong ki, namar ba ki la leit wad ïa ki blei ka Edom:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> kumta, u Joash u syiem ki Israel u la leit kiew; bad ma u bad u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah ki la ïakhmih kai markhmat ha Beth-shemesh, kaba dei ïa ka Judah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ïa ki Judah la jop ha khmat ki Israel, bad ki la phet ïap uwei uwei baroh sha la ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Joash u syiem ki Israel u la kem ïa u Amasaïah u syiem ka Judah, u khun u Joash u khun u Jehoahas, ha Beth-shemesh, bad u la wallam ïa u sha Jerusalem, bad u la pynkyllon ïa ka kynroh ka Jerusalem naduh ka khyrdop Ephraim haduh ka khyrdop ka dong, sawspah pruh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u la shim ïa ka ksiar bad ka rupa baroh, bad ïa ki pliang baroh kat ïa kiba la shem ha ka ïing U Blei bad u Obed-edom, bad ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïingsyiem, bad ïa ki nongbahjamin ruh, bad u la leit phai sha Samaria.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Amasaïah u khun u Joash u syiem ka Judah u la im sa khatsan snem hadien ka jingïap u Joash u khun u Jehoahas u syiem ki Israel.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Amasaïah, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, ha khmih, ym shym la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Judah bad Ki Syiem Israel?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te naduh kata ka por ba u Amasaïah u la phai noh na kaba bud ïa U Trai ki la pynlong ka jingïashet pyrshah ïa u ha Jerusalem; te u la phet ïap sha Lakhish: hynrei, ki la phah beh ïa u sha Lakhish, bad ki la pynïap ïa u hangta.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki la wallam ïa u halor ki kulai, bad ki la tep ïa u bad la ki kpa ha ka nongbah jong ka Judah."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u paidbah Judah baroh u la shim ïa u Ussiah, uba la khathynriew snem ka rta, bad ki la thung syiem ïa u ha ka jaka u kpa jong u, u Amasaïah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U la tei ïa ka Eloth, bad u la pynïoh pat ïa ka sha ki Judah, hadien kata, u syiem u la thiah bad la ki kpa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Ussiah u la long khathynriew snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar sanphew ar snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Jekoliah” kaba na Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, katba kum kata baroh ba u kpa jong u, u Amasaïah u la leh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la aiti ïa lade ban wad ïa U Blei ha ki sngi jong u Sekharaïah, uba don ka jingsngewthuh ha ki jingithuhpaw ki jong U Blei: bad katba u la dang wad ïa U Trai, U Blei u la pynman bha ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u la mih noh bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Philistia, bad u la pynkyllon ïa ka kynroh jong ka Gath, bad ïa ka kynroh jong ka Jabneh, bad ïa ka kynroh jong ka Ashdod; bad u la tei ki nongbah ha ka ri Ashdod, bad hapdeng ki Philistia.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te U Blei u la ïarap ïa u pyrshah ïa ki Philistia, bad pyrshah ïa ki Arab kiba shong ha Gur-baal, bad ïa ki nong Meun.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki Ammon ki la ai ki jingai sngewbha ïa u Ussiah: bad ka nam jong u ka la phriang kylleng wat shaduh khap Ijipt; naba u la man khraw bor shibun.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Ussiah u la tei ruh ïa ki ïing phira ha Jerusalem ha ka khyrdop ka dong, bad ha Ka Khyrdop Ka Them, bad kaba ha kaba khun ka kynroh, bad u la pynskhem ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la tei ruh ïa ki ïing phira ha ka ri khlaw, bad u la tih shibun ki pukri: naba u la don shibun ki jingri, ha ka ri them bad ha ka ri madan; bad u la don ki nongrep bad ki nongsumar brisoh Waiñ ha ki lum bad ha ki lyngkha basei soh; naba u sngewbha ïa ka jingrep.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Ussiah u la don ruh shi paidbah ki nongïapom, kiba mih noh sha ka thma ha la ki kynhun kynhun, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ka jingñiew ïa kiba la thaw da u Jeiel u nongthoh bad u Maaseïah u rangbah, hapoh ka jingsumar u Hananiah, uwei na ki kaptan jong u syiem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka jingkheiñ baroh jong ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, ka jong ki riewkhlaiñ bashlur, ka la long ar hajar hynriewspah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad hapoh ka jingsumar jong ki la don ka kynhun shipai ba la hikai, laispah hynñiew hajar sanspah, kiba ïaleh thma da ka bor bakhraw, ban ïarap ïa u syiem pyrshah ïa ki nongshun.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Ussiah u la khreh na ka bynta jong ki, na ka bynta ki paidïapom baroh keiñ, ki stieh, bad ki sum, bad ki jingïada khlieh, bad ki jingphong nar, bad ki ryntieh, bad ki maw ban kawang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la thaw ki kor ha Jerusalem, ïa kiba la shem da ki riewproh jingmut, ban buh halor ki ïing phira bad halor ki kynroh ïada, ïa ka ban siat khnam bad ïa ki maw ki bakhraw da ki. Te ka nam jong u ka la phriang kylleng sawdong, naba la ïarap ïa u da kaba phylla shibun, naduh ba u la man khraw bor.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, haba u la man khraw bor, ka dohnud jong u ka la meng kat ïa ka ban sniew, bad u la leh palat ïa U Trai U Blei jong u; naba u la leit rung ha ka templ jong U Trai ban thang jingiwbih halor ka duwan ba thang jingiwbih.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Asaraïah lyngdoh u la leit rung hadien jong u, bad phraphew ngut ki lyngdoh jong U Trai lem bad u, kiba long ki riewshlur:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ki la ïaïeng pyrshah ïa u syiem Ussiah, bad ki la ong ha u, “Ym dei ka jong me, ko Ussiah, ban thang jingiwbih ha U Trai, hynrei, ka jong ki lyngdoh hi ki khun u Aaron, ïa kiba la pynkyntang ban thang jingiwbih: to mih noh na ka jaka kyntang; naba me la leh palat; lymne kan ym long burom ïa me na U Trai U Blei.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, u Ussiah u la bitar; te u la don ka pliang ha ka kti jong u ban thang jingiwbih; bad katba u la bitar ïa ki lyngdoh, u 'ñiangthohlieh u la mih ha ka shyllangmat jong u ha khmat ki lyngdoh ha ka ïing U Trai, hajan ka duwan ba thang jingiwbih.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Asaraïah u rangbah lyngdoh, bad ki lyngdoh baroh, ki la khmih ha u, te ha khmih, u la sa 'ñiangthohlieh na ka shyllangmat, bad ki la shop noh ïa u nangta kloi kloi; shisha, u hi ruh u la mih noh kyrkieh, namar U Trai u la shoh ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u syiem Ussiah u la long u bapang 'thohlieh haduh ka sngi ka jingïap jong u, bad u la shong ha ka ïing kaba kyrpang, u da long u bapang 'thohlieh; naba la ot noh ïa u na ka ïing U Trai: bad u Jotham u khun jong u, u la long halor ka ïingsyiem, u da bishar ïa ki briew jong kata ka ri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Ussiah, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, la thoh da u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa, u khun u Amos.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, u Ussiah u la thiah bad la ki kpa; bad ki la tep ïa u bad la ki kpa ha ka jaka tep briew ki syiem; naba ki ong, “U long u bapang 'thohlieh”; bad u Jotham u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Jotham u la long arphew san snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khathynriew snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Jerushah” ka khun u Sadok.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, katba kum kata baroh ba u kpa jong u, u Ussiah u la leh: hynrei, um shym la leit rung ha ka ïing U Trai. Te ki paidbah ki shu dang leh sniew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U la tei ïa ka khyrdop kaba haneng ka ïing U Trai, bad halor ka kynroh Ophel u la tei shibun.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U la tei ruh ïa ki nongbah ha ka ri lum Judah, bad ki khlaw u la tei ki ïing kut bad ki ïing phira.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la ïaleh ruh ïa u syiem ki khun u Ammon, bad u la jop ïa ki. Bad ki khun u Ammon ki la ai ha kata kajuh ka snem shispah talent ka rupa, bad shiphew hajar byrni u Kew, bad shiphew hajar u Barli. Katta hi ki khun u Ammon ki la ai ha u, ha ka snem ka ba-ar, bad ha ka balai ruh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u Jotham u la man khraw namar u la pynbeit la ki lynti ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam u Jotham, bad ki thma jong u baroh, bad ki lynti jong u, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Israel bad Judah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U la long arphew san snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar, bad u la synshar khathynriew snem ha Jerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jotham u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka shnong u Dabid: te u Ahas u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Ahas u la arphew snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khathynriew snem ha Jerusalem: bad um shym la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, kum u Dabid u kpa jong u:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> hynrei, u la ïaid ha ki lynti ki syiem ki Israel, bad u la thaw ruh ki dur ba la saiñ ïa ki Baal.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la thang ïa ka jingiwbih ha ka them u khun u Hinnom, bad u la thang ïa la ki khun ha ka ding, katba kum ki jingijli jong ki nongmane bleithaw, ïa kiba U Trai u la beh noh na khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la kñia bad u la thang ka jingiwbih ha ki jaka bajrong, bad halor ki lum, bad hapoh u dieng bajyrngam baroh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, U Trai U Blei jong u, u la ai noh ïa u ha ka kti u syiem ka Syria; bad ki la jop ïa u, bad ki la ïalam mraw noh ïa u paidbah babun na ki jong u, bad ki la wallam ïa ki sha Damaskos. Bad la aiti noh ruh ïa u ha u syiem ki Israel, uba la jop ïa u da ka jingpynïap bakhraw.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Naba u Pekah u khun u Remaliah u la pynïap ha Judah ha kawei hi ka sngi shispah arphew hajar, kita baroh ki briew bashlur; namar ba ki la kyntait noh ïa U Trai, U Blei jong ki kpa jong ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Sikhri, u briew badonbor uba na Ephraim, u la pynïap ïa u Maaseïah u khun jong u syiem, bad ïa u Asrikam u nongsynshar jong ka ïing, bad ïa u Elkanah uba hajan eh ïa u syiem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ring mraw ïa la ki para, arspah hajar, ki kynthei, ki khun shynrang, bad ki khun kynthei, bad ki la shim ruh shibun ka jinglute na ki, bad ki la wallam ïa kata ka jinglute sha Samaria.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u nongïathuhlypa jong U Trai u la don hangta, uba ka kyrteng jong u ka long “u Oded”: bad u la leit tan ïa u paidïapom uba la wan sha Samaria, bad u la ong ha ki, “Ha khmih, namar ba U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong phi, u la bitar ïa ki Judah, u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong phi, bad phi la pynïap ïa ki ha ka jingbitar kaba la poi tiap haduh bneng.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te mynta phi thmu ban pynpoh ïa ki khun Judah bad ki Jerusalem ban long ki mraw shynrang bad ki mraw kynthei ha phi; hynrei, wat ha phi hi ym don ki jingpalat ki jong phi pyrshah ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata te, to sngap ïa nga, bad to phah noh pat ïa kine ki mraw, kiba phi la kem mraw na la ki para: naba ka jingbitar ba-itieng ka jong U Trai ka long halor jong phi.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te katto katne na ki rangbah ki khun u Ephraim, u Asaraïah u khun u Johanan, u Berekhaïah u khun u Meshilemoth, bad u Jehiskiah u khun u Shallum, bad u Amasa u khun u Hadlai, ki la ïeng pyrshah ïa kita kiba la wan na ka thma,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ki la ong ha ki, “Phin ym wallam hapoh hangne ïa kita ki mraw: naba phi thmu ïa kata ka ban wallam halor jong ngi ïa ka jingpalat pyrshah ïa U Trai, ban nang kynton halor ki pop jong ngi bad halor ka jingpalat jong ngi: naba ka jingpalat jong ngi ka long ka bakhraw, bad don ka jingbitar ba-itieng pyrshah ïa ki Israel.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, kita ki briew ba la kieng atiar ki la iehnoh ïa kita ki mraw bad ïa kata ka jinglute ha khmat kita ki rangbah bad u paidlang baroh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kita ki briew kiba la ïathuh da ka kyrteng ki la ïeng joit, bad ki la shim ïa kita ki mraw, bad ki la pynkup ïa kiba lyngkhuit baroh hapdeng jong ki da kata ka jinglute, bad ki la pynkup jaiñ ïa ki, bad ki la pynphong juti ïa ki, bad ki la ai ha ki ban bam bad ban dih, bad ki la pynsleh ïa ki, bad kynja ïa ki batlot baroh na ki, ki la pynshong halor ki kadda, bad ki la wallam ïa ki sha Jerikho, ka shnong ki dieng Tlai, ha ki para jong ki: ynda kumta, ki la leit phai pat sha Samaria.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha kata ka por, u syiem Ahas u la phah pan na ki syiem ka Assyria ba kin ïarap ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba sa ki Edom pat ki la wan bad ki la shoh tangon ïa ki Judah, bad ki la ring mraw noh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki Philistia ruh ki la hiar thma ïa ki shnong jong ka ri them, bad ïa kaba shathie ka Judah, bad ki la jop ïa ka Beth-shemesh bad ïa ka Aijalon, bad ïa ka Gederoth, bad ïa ka Soko bad ki shnong jong ka, ïa ka Timnah bad ïa ki shnong jong ka, bad ïa ka Gimso ruh bad ïa ki shnong jong ka: bad ki la shong hangta.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Naba U Trai u la pynpoh ïa ka Judah na ka bynta u Ahas u syiem ki Israel; naba u la leh pathar ha Judah, bad u la leh palat jur ïa U Trai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Tilgath-pilneser u syiem ka Assyria u la wan sha u, bad u la pynjynjar ïa u, hynrei, um shym la ïashan bor ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Namar u Ahas u la shim noh shi bynta na ka ïing U Trai, bad na ka ïing u syiem bad ka jong ki rangbah, bad u la ai ïa ka ha u syiem ka Assyria: hynrei, um shym ïarap satia ïa u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ha ka por ka jingjynjar jong u, u la nang leh palat shuh shuh ïa U Trai, une u syiem Ahas keiñ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Naba u la kñia ha ki blei jong ka Damaskos, kiba la shoh tangon ïa u: bad u la ong, “Namar ba ki blei jong ki syiem ka Syria ki la ïarap ïa ki, namar kata, ngan kñia ha ki, ba kin dup ïarap ïa nga.” Hynrei, ki la long ka jingjot ïa u, bad ïa baroh ki Israel.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Ahas la ïalum lang ïa ki khiew ki pliang ka ïing U Blei, bad u la ot lyngkhot lyngkhot ïa ki khiew ki pliang ka ïing U Blei, bad u la khang ïa ki jingkhang ka ïing U Trai; bad u la thaw ïa lade ki duwan ha ka dong baroh jong ka Jerusalem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ha ka shnong baroh jong ka Judah u la thaw ki jaka bajrong ban thang ïa ka jingiwbih ha kiwei pat ki blei, bad u la pynkhih bitar ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te kiba dang sah na ki kam jong u, bad baroh ki lynti jong u, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Judah bad Israel.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Ahas u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka nongbah, ha Jerusalem keiñ; namar kim shym la wallam ïa u sha ki jingtep ki syiem ki Israel: bad u Hesekaïah u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Hesekaïah u la sdang ban synshar haba u la arphew san snem ka rta; bad u la synshar arphew khyndai snem ha Jerusalem: bad ka kyrteng ka kmie jong u ka la long “ka Abijah” ka khun u Sekharaïah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, kat kum kaba u Dabid u kpa jong u, u la leh baroh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ha ka banyngkong ka snem ka jingsynshar jong u, ha u bnai u banyngkong, u la plie ïa ki jingkhang ka ïing U Trai, bad u la shna bha pat ïa ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la wallam hapoh ïa ki lyngdoh bad ïa ki Lebi; bad u la ïalum lang ïa ki ha ka jaka kaba kylluid shaphang mihngi, bad u la ong ha ki,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “To sngew ïa nga, phi ki Lebi, mynta to phin pynkyntang ïa lade, bad to pynkyntang ïa ka ïing U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong phi, bad to kit noh ïa ka jingjakhlia na ka jaka bakhuid.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Naba ki kpa jong ngi ki la leh palat, bad ki la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong ngi, bad ki la kyntait noh ïa u, bad ki la phai noh ïa la ki khmat na ka jaka shong U Trai, bad ki la phai ïa la ki ingdong.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki la khang noh ruh ïa ki jingkhang ka batsha, bad ki la pynlip ïa ki sharak, bad kim shym thang ïa ki jingiwbih lymne ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang ha ka jaka bakhuid ha U Blei jong ki Israel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Namar kata, ka jingbitar U Trai ka la long halor ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem, bad u la ai noh ïa ki ban long ïa kiba la pynshad phaloh shane bad shawei, ban long ka jinglyngngoh, bad ka jingkynshi, kumba phi ïohi da la ki khmat.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Naba ha khmih, ki kpa jong ngi ki la kyllon da ka waitlam, bad ki khun shynrang jong ngi, bad ki khun kynthei jong ngi bad ki tnga jong ngi ki don ha ka jinglongmraw namar kane.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mynta te, ka don ha ka dohnud jong nga ban thaw ka jutang bad U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ba ka jingbitar ba-itieng jong u kan phai noh na ngi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ko ki khun shynrang jong nga, wat long mynta ki bymsuidñiew: naba U Trai u la jied ïa phi ban ïeng ha khmat jong u, ban shakri ïa u, bad ba phin long ki nongkam jong u, bad ban thang ïa ka jingiwbih.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki Lebi ki la ïeng joit, u Mahath u khun u Amasai, bad u Joel u khun u Asaraïah, na ki khun jong ki Kohath; bad na ki khun u Merari: u Kish u khun u Abdi, bad u Asaraïah u khun u Jehallelil; bad na ki Gershon: u Joah u khun u Simmah, bad u Eden u khun u Joah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad na ki khun u Elisaphan: u Shimri bad u Jeiel; bad na ki khun u Asaph: u Sekharaïah bad u Mathaniah:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad na ki khun u Heman: u Jehiel bad u Shimei; bad na ki khun u Jeduthun: u Shemaïah bad u Ussiel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki la ïalum ïa la ki para, bad ki la pynkyntang ïa lade, bad ki la leit shapoh, katba kum ka hukum u syiem da ki ktien jong U Trai, ban pynkhuid ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki lyngdoh ki la leit rung sha ka bynta ba kham shapoh jong ka ïing U Trai, ban pynkhuid ïa ka, bad ki la sei shabar ïa ka jingbymkhuid baroh kaba ki la shem hapoh ka templ jong U Trai sha ka phyllaw jong ka ïing U Trai. Te ki Lebi ki la shim ïa ka, ban leit kit noh shabar sha ka wah duid Kidron.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki la sdang ha ka shi tarik jong u bnai u banyngkong ban pynkhuid, bad ha ka baphra tarik jong uta u bnai ki la wan sha ka batsha jong U Trai; bad phra sngi ki la pynkhuid ïa ka ïing U Trai: bad ha ka bakhathynriew tarik jong u bnai u banyngkong ki la pyndep phar.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la leit ha u syiem Hesekaïah shapoh ka ïing, bad ki la ong, “Ngi la pynkhuid ïa ka ïing U Trai baroh, bad ïa ka duwan ka jingainguh thang, lem bad ki kynja pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka miej u 'pu pyni, lem bad ki kynja pliang jong ka baroh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ïa ki kynja pliang baroh ruh, ïa kiba u syiem Ahas ha ka jingsynshar jong u, u la bred noh haba u la leh palat, ngi la pynkhreh bad ngi la pynkhuid; bad ha khmih, ki don ha khmat ka duwan U Trai.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem Hesekaïah u la khie la dang step, bad u la ïalum ïa ki rangbah ka shnong, bad u la leit kiew sha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki la wallam hynñiew tylli ki masi dab, bad hynñiew tylli ki langbrot shynrang, bad hynñiew tylli ki khun langbrot, bad hynñiew tylli ki 'lang sohmoh, ïa ka jingainguh pop na ka bynta ka hima bad na ka bynta ka jaka kyntang bad na ka bynta ka Judah. Te u la hukum ïa ki lyngdoh ki khun u Aaron ban ainguh ïa ki halor ka duwan U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, ki la pynïap ïa ki masi dab, bad ki lyngdoh ki la pdiang ïa ka snam, bad ki la synreit ïa ka halor ka duwan: bad ki la pynïap ïa ki langbrot shynrang, bad ki la synreit ïa ka snam halor ka duwan: ki la pynïap ïa ki khun langbrot ruh, bad ki la synreit ïa ka snam halor ka duwan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la wallam hajan ïa ki 'lang sohmoh ïa ka jingainguh pop ha khmat u syiem bad u paidlang; bad ki la buh ïa la ki kti halor jong ki;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad ki lyngdoh ki la pynïap ïa ki, bad ki la pynlong ka jingainguh pop da ka snam jong ki halor ka duwan, ban pynlong ka kuna na ka bynta ki Israel baroh: naba u syiem u la hukum ba ïa ka jingainguh thang bad ïa ka jingainguh pop dei ban pynlong na ka bynta ki Israel baroh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u la buh ïa ki Lebi ha ka ïing U Trai bad ki shakuriaw, bad ki nebel, bad ki duitara de, kat kum ka hukum jong u Dabid, bad ka jong u Gad u nongïohi jong u syiem, bad u Nathan u nongïathuhlypa: namar ka hukum ka la long na U Trai da ki nongïathuhlypa jong U.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ki Lebi ki la ïeng bad ki jingtem jong u Dabid, bad ki lyngdoh lem bad ki jingput.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la hukum ban ainguh ïa ka jingainguh thang halor ka duwan. Bad haba ka jingainguh thang ka la sdang, ka jingrwai U Trai ruh ka la sdang, bad ki jingput, lem bad ki jingtem jong u Dabid u syiem ki Israel.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad baroh u paidlang u la mane dem, bad ki nongrwai ki la rwai, bad ki nongput ki la put; kane baroh ka la ïaineh haduh ban da la pyndep ïa ka jingainguh thang.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te haba ki la pyndep ïa ka jingainguh, u syiem bad baroh kiba don lem bad u ki la dem ïa lade bad ki la mane.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u syiem Hesekaïah bad ki rangbah ki la hukum ruh ïa ki Lebi ban rwai ki jingïaroh ha U Trai da ki ktien jong u Dabid, bad ki jong u Asaph u nongïohi. Te ki la rwai ïa ki jingïaroh da kaba kmen, bad ki la dem ïa la ki khlieh bad ki la mane.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, u Hesekaïah u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Mynta phi la pynkyntang ïa lade ha U Trai, to ale hajan bad wallam ïa ki jingkñia bad ïa ki jingainguh ha ka ïing U Trai.” Te u paidlang u la wallam ïa ki jingkñia bad ïa ki jingainguh; bad kat kiba mon sngewbha hi ki la wallam ïa ki jingainguh thang.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ka jingkheiñ ïa ki jingainguh thang, kiba la wallam u paidlang, ka la long hynñiewphew tylli ki masi dab, shispah tylli ki langbrot shynrang, bad arspah tylli ki khun langbrot: kine baroh ki la long na ka bynta ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad kiei kiei kiba la pynkyntang ki la long hynriewspah tylli ki masi dab bad lai hajar ki langbrot.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, ki lyngdoh ki la long khyndiat eh, kumta kim lah puid snieh shuh ïa ki jingainguh thang baroh, namar kata, ki para jong ki, ki Lebi ki la ïarap ïa ki, haduh ban da la pyndep ïa ka kam, bad haduh ban da ki lyngdoh ki la lah pynkhuid ïa lade; naba ki Lebi ki la long kham beit ka dohnud ban pynkhuid ïa lade ban ïa ki lyngdoh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ki jingainguh thang ruh ki la bun eh, lem bad ka khleiñ jong ki jingainguh pynïasuk, bad ki jingainguh dih na ka bynta man la ka jingainguh thang. Kumta, la buh beit ïa ka jingshakri ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la leh kmen, bad u paidbah baroh, na ka bynta kata kaba U Blei u la pynkhreh ïa u paidbah: naba la leh ïa kane shisyndon noh."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Hesekaïah u la phah ha ki Israel bad ki Judah baroh, bad u la thoh shithi ruh ha ki Ephraim bad ha ki Manasseh, ba kin wan ha ka ïing U Trai ha Jerusalem, ban rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Naba u syiem u la ïasylla bad ki rangbah, bad u paidlang baroh ha Jerusalem, ban rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha u bnai u ba-ar.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Naba kim lah ban rakhe ïa ka ha kata ka por, namar kat ban biang na ki lyngdoh kim pat shym pynkyntang ïa lade, bad ki briew ruh kim pat shym ïalang ha Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kane ka la idei ha khmat u syiem bad u paidlang baroh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, ki la pynskhem ïa ka rai ban pynbna ha Israel baroh, naduh Beer-sheba haduh Dan, ba kin wan ban rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ha Jerusalem: namar kim shym la rakhe la slem eh ha ka rukom kumba la thoh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta ki dak ki la leit bad ki shithi na u syiem bad ki rangbah jong u baroh sawdong ka ri Israel bad ka ri Judah, bad katba kum ka hukum u syiem, ki ïa-ong, “Phi ki khun Israel, to phai pat sha U Trai, U Blei u Abraham, u Isaak, bad u Israel, ba u ruh un wan phai ha ita i bynta ba sah kiba la lait im na ka kti ki syiem ka Assyria.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad to wat long phi kum ki kpa jong phi, bad kum ki para jong phi, kiba la leh palat ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki, kumta ba u la aiti noh ïa ki ban long ka jingkynjah, kumba phi ïohi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Phi te to wat long kiba la pyneh ryndang, kumba ki kpa jong phi ki la long; hynrei, to pynkohnguh ïa lade ha U Trai, bad to rung ruh hapoh ka jaka kyntang jong u, ïa kaba u la pynkyntang junom, bad to shakri ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi, ba ka jingbitar ba-itieng jong u kan phai noh na phi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar lada phin phai pat sha U Trai, ki para jong phi bad ki khun jong phi kin shem ka jingsngewsynei na kita kiba la ring mraw ïa ki, bad kin ïoh wan pat sha kane ka ri: naba U Trai U Blei jong phi u long uba aiei bad uba isynei, bad un ym phai noh la ka khmat na phi, lada phi phai sha u.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta ki dak ki la ïaid na ka shnong sha ka shnong ha ka ri Ephraim bad Manasseh, haduh Sabulon keiñ: hynrei, ki la rkhiebeiñ ïa ki, bad ki la pyrthuhbeiñ ïa ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Pynban, bun kiba na ki Asher bad Manasseh bad Sabulon ki la pynrit ïa lade, bad ki la wan sha Jerusalem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ha Judah ruh ka kti jong U Blei ka la don ban ai ïa ki kawei ka dohnud, ban leh ïa ka hukum u syiem bad ki rangbah da ka ktien U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad la ïalum lang shibun ki briew ha Jerusalem ban rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat ha u bnai u ba-ar, u paidbah bakhraw eh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la ïeng bad ki la shim noh ïa ki duwan kiba la don ha Jerusalem, bad ki la shim noh ïa ki duwan jingiwbih baroh, bad ki la bred ïa ki sha ka wah duid Kidron.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la pynïap ïa Ka Jinglait ha ka bakhatsaw sngi u bnai u ba-ar: bad ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ki la lehrain, bad ki la pynkyntang ïa lade, bad ki la wallam ïa ki jingainguh thang ha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki la ïeng ha la ki jaka ha la ka kam ka kam, katba kum ka hukum u Moses u briew jong U Blei: ki lyngdoh ki la synreit ïa ka snam, ïa kaba ki la ïoh na ka kti ki Lebi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar ba don bun ha ka jingïaseng ki bym pat shym pynkyntang ïa lade: namar kata, ki Lebi ki la dei ban pynïap ïa Ki Jinglait na ka bynta uwei uwei baroh u bymkhuid, ban pynkyntang ïa ki ha U Trai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Naba u paidbah babun, bun na Ephraim keiñ bad Manasseh, Issakhar bad Sabulon, kim shym pat la pynkhuid ïa lade, pynban, ki la bam ïa Ka Jinglait da kumwei pat na kaba la thoh. Naba u Hesekaïah u la lah duwai na ka bynta jong ki, u da ong,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “To U Trai u babha un map ïa uwei pa uwei uba buh la ka dohnud ban wad ïa U Blei, U Trai, U Blei jong ki kpa jong u, la ym shym la pynkhuid ïa u katba kum ka jingpynkhuid ka jaka kyntang.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad U Trai u la sngap ïa u Hesekaïah, bad u la pynkhiah ïa u paidbah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki khun Israel kiba la don ha Jerusalem ki la rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat, hynñiew sngi da ka jingkmen bakhraw: bad ki Lebi bad ki lyngdoh ki la ïaroh ïa U Trai man la ka sngi, da kaba rwai bad ki jingtem bajam ha U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Hesekaïah u la kren sngewbha ha ki Lebi baroh kiba la nang bha ha ka jingshakri ïa U Trai. Kumta, ki la bam ha Ka Jingkhawai, baroh hynñiew sngi, ki da ainguh ki jingkñia bapynïasuk, bad ki da pynlong ka jingphla ha U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ka jingïaseng baroh ka la ïasylla ban rakhe sa ïa kiwei pat ki hynñiew sngi: bad ki la rakhe ïa kiwei pat ki hynñiew sngi da ka jingkmen.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Naba u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah u la lah ai ha ka jingïaseng ban long ki jingainguh, shi hajar ki masi dab bad hynñiew hajar ki langbrot; bad ki rangbah ki la ai ha ka jingïaseng, shi hajar ki masi dab bad shiphew hajar ki langbrot: bad shibun bah ki lyngdoh ki la pynkyntang ïa lade.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u paidbah Judah baroh, lem bad ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, bad u paidbah baroh ba la mih noh na Israel, bad ki nongwei kiba la wan noh na ri Israel, bad kiba la shong ha Judah, ki la kmen.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumta, la long ka jingkmen bakhraw ha Jerusalem: naba naduh ka por u Solomon u khun u Dabid u syiem ki Israel ym shym la don kaba kum kata ha Jerusalem.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ki lyngdoh ki Lebi ki la ïeng bad ki la kyrkhu ïa ki paidbah: bad la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien jong ki, bad ka jingduwai jong ki ka la kiew haduh ka jaka shong bakhuid jong u, shaduh bneng keiñ."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba ïa kane baroh la pyndep, baroh ki Israel kiba ïadon ki la leit noh sha ki shnong Judah, bad ki la pyntwa ïa ki mawbynna, bad ki la pynngat ïa ki Asherah, bad ki la pynduh ïa ki jaka bajrong bad ïa ki duwan na Judah bad Benjamin baroh, ha Ephraim ruh bad Manasseh, haduh ba ki la pynjot ïa ki baroh. Hadien kata, ki khun Israel baroh ki la leit wan noh, uwei uwei baroh sha la ka bynta, sha la ki jong ki shnong.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Hesekaïah u la buh ïa ki jingkylliang sngi jong ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ha la ki jingkylliang sngi jong ki, uwei uwei u briew baroh katba kum ha ka kam jong u, ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ruh, ïa ki jingainguh thang bad ki jingkñia bapynïasuk, ban shakri, bad ban ainguh, bad ban ïaroh ha ki khyrdop ka ïingjaiñ U Trai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U la buh ruh ïa ka bynta u syiem na kaba u don ïa ki jingainguh thang, kata, ïa ka jingainguh thang mynstep bad janmiet, bad ki jingainguh thang ki Sabbaton, bad ïa ki 'nai thymmai, bad ïa Ki Jingkhawai Niam ba la buh, kumba la thoh ha Ka Hukum U Trai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nalor kata, u la hukum ïa ki briew kiba shong ha Jerusalem ban ai ïa ka bynta jong ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, ba ki lah ban aiti ïa lade ha Ka Hukum U Trai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba dang shu lah pynbna ïa ka hukum, ki khun Israel ki la ai kyrhai ïa ki soh nyngkong u Kew, ka Waiñ, bad ka umphniang, bad ka ngap, bad na ka jingmih jong ka lyngkha baroh; bad ïa kaba shiphew na kiei kiei baroh ki la wallam kyrhai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki khun Israel bad Judah, kiba shong ha ki shnong Judah, ki ruh ki la wallam ïa kaba shiphew na ki masi dab bad ki langbrot, bad kaba shiphew na kiei kiei ba la pynkyntang kiba la kyntang ha U Trai U Blei jong ki, bad ki la buh kynton ïa ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ha u bnai u balai ki la sdang ban buh ïa ka nongrim jong kine ki kynton, bad ki la pyndep ïa ki ha u bnai u bahynñiew.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te haba u Hesekaïah bad ki rangbah, ki la wan bad ki la ïohi ïa ki kynton, ki la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, bad ïa u paidlang jong u ki Israel.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la kylli jingkylli bad ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi shaphang ki kynton.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Asaraïah u rangbah lyngdoh, na ka ïing u Sadok, u la ïathuh ïa u bad u la ong, “Naduh ba ki briew ki la sdang ban wallam ïa ki jingainguh shapoh ka ïing U Trai, ngi la bam bad ngi la kdang, bad la pyntam shibun: namar U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa la ki briew; bad kata kaba la tam long kane ka jingkynshew bakhraw.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la hukum ban pynlong ki kamra ha ka ïing U Trai; bad ki la pynlong ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la wallam beit ïa ki jingainguh bad ïa kiba shiphew bad ïa kiei kiei ba la pynkyntang: bad u Konaniah u Lebi u la long u nongsynshar halor jong ki, bad u Shimei u para jong u, u la long uba bud.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Jehiel, bad u Asasiah, bad u Nahath, bad u Asahel, bad u Jerimoth, bad u Josabad, bad u Eliel, bad u Ismakhiah, bad u Mahath, bad u Benaïah, ki la long ki sordar hapoh u Konaniah bad u Shimei u para jong u, da kaba u la thung u Hesekaïah u syiem, bad u Asaraïah u nongsynshar ka ïing U Blei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Kore u khun u Imnah u kynja Lebi, u nongap Ka Khyrdop Mihngi, u la long halor ki jingainguh ka mon sngewbha jong U Blei, ban ïasam ïa ki jingkñia jong U Trai, bad ïa kiei kiei ki bakyntang tam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad hapoh jong u la don u Eden, bad u Miniamin, bad u Jeshua, bad u Shemaïah, u Amariah, bad u Shekaniah, ha ki nongbah ki lyngdoh, ha ki kam ba la buh jong ki, ban ai ha la ki para kylliang kylliang, ha kiba khraw kumjuh ha kiba rit ruh kumjuh:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> nalor kita ki shynrang kiba la kheiñ da ka jinghiar pateng, naduh kiba lai snem bad tam ruh, uwei uwei baroh keiñ uba la rung ha ïing U Trai, katba kum ka jingdonkam ka kam kaba ha la ka sngi, ïa ka jingshakri jong ki ha ka jingkam jong ki katba kum ka jingïakylliang jong ki;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad kita kiba la kheiñ da ki jinghiar pateng jong ki lyngdoh da ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, bad ki Lebi naduh kiba arphew snem bad tam ruh, ha ki jingkam jong ki kylliang kylliang;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad kita kiba la kheiñ da ka jinghiar pateng ki khun rit jong ki, ki tnga jong ki, bad ki khun shynrang jong ki, bad ki khun kynthei jong ki, ha ka jingïaseng baroh: namar ki la pynkyntang ïa lade ha ka jingkhuid ïa ka kam ba la buh:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ïa ki khun shynrang u Aaron ki lyngdoh ruh, kiba la don ha ki lyngkha ki rudnong ki nongbah jong ki, ha kawei pa kawei ka nongbah baroh, ki la don ki rangbah kiba la ïathuh kyrteng, ban ai ki bynta ïa ki shynrang baroh hapdeng ki lyngdoh, bad ha kita baroh kiba la kheiñ da ka jinghiar pateng hapdeng ki Lebi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Hesekaïah u la leh kumne ha ka ri Judah baroh kawei; bad u la leh ïa kata ka babha bad kaba dei bad kaba shisha ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ha kano kano ka kam ba u la sdang ha ka jingshakri ka ïing U Blei, bad ha ka aiñ, bad ha ki hukum, ban wad ïa U Blei jong u, u la leh ïa kata da la ka dohnud baroh, bad u la man bha."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kine kiei kiei, bad kane ka jingshisha, u Sennakherib u syiem ka Assyria u la wan, bad u la rung ha Judah, bad u la shong dara ban ïaleh ïa ki shnong ba ker kynroh, bad u la mut ban jop ïa ki ha lade.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba u Hesekaïah u la ïohi ba u Sennakherib u la wan, bad ba u la thew ban ïaleh ïa ka Jerusalem,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u la ïasylla bad la ki rangbah bad la ki briew badonbor ban set ïa ki um jong ki umpohliew kiba la don shabar ka nongbah; te ki la ïarap ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, la ïalum shibun ki briew, bad ki la set baroh ki umpohliew, bad ïa ka wah duid kaba tuid napdeng ka ri, ki ïa-ong, “Balei ki syiem ka Assyria kin wan bad kin shem shibun ka um?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la sngewshlur, bad u la tei baroh ka kynroh kaba la twa, bad u la pynjrong ïa ka haduh ki ïing phira, bad ïa kata kawei pat ka kynroh shabar, bad u la pynskhem ïa ka Millo ha ka nongbah u Dabid, bad u la thaw ki tiar ïapom bad ki stieh shibun eh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la thung ki kaptan ïapom halor ki paidbah, bad u la ïalum lang ïa ki ha u ha ka jaka bakylluid ha ka khyrdop jong ka nongbah, bad u la kren pynshngain ha ki, u da ong,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “To long kiba shynrang bad kiba shlur, wat sheptieng lymne wat khaw-eit namar u syiem ka Assyria, lymne namar u paidbah baroh uba don bad u: namar don uba kham khraw bad ngi ban ïa kaba bad u:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u ka don ka ksang'ti doh; hynrei, bad ngi u don U Trai U Blei jong ngi ban ïarap ïa ngi, bad ban ïaleh ïa ki jingïaleh thma jong ngi.” Te ki paidbah ki la shaniah ha ki ktien u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hadien kane, u Sennakherib u syiem ka Assyria u la phah ïa la ki shakri sha Jerusalem, (te u la don ha khmat ka Lakhish, bad baroh ka bor jong u lem bad u,) ha u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah, bad ha ki Judah baroh kiba don ha Jerusalem, ki ïa-ong,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Kumne u ong u Sennakherib u syiem ka Assyria, ‘Ha-ei phi shaniah, ba phi shu shah ïa ka jingker kut ha Jerusalem?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Hesekaïah um pynkohnguh ïa phi mo, ban aiti ïa phi ban ïap da ka 'nemsniew bad da ka jingsliang, da kaba ong, “U Trai U Blei jong ngi un pyllait ïa ngi na ka kti u syiem ka Assyria?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Uta hi u Hesekaïah um shym la pynduh noh ïa ki jaka bajrong jong u bad ïa ki duwan jong u, bad u la hukum ïa ka Judah bad ïa ka Jerusalem, u da ong, “Phin mane ha khmat kawei ka duwan, bad halor jong ka phin thang ka jingiwbih?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Phim tip ïa kaei ba nga bad ki kpa jong nga ngi la leh ha ki briew baroh jong ki ri? Ki blei jong ki jaid bynriew jong ki ri ki la lah kumno kumno ban pyllait ïa ki ri jong ki na ka kti jong nga?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Uei napdeng ki blei baroh jong kito ki jaid bynriew ïa kiba ki kpa jong nga ki la pynjot khoit, uba la lah ban pyllait noh ïa ki briew jong u na ka kti jong nga, ba U Blei jong phi un lah ban pyllait noh ïa phi na ka kti jong nga?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Namar kata te, wat shah ïa u Hesekaïah ban shukor ïa phi, lymne pynkohnguh ïa phi ha kane ka rukom, lymne phi wat ngeit ïa u: namar ym don blei na kano kano ka jaid bynriew lane ka hima uba lah ban pyllait noh ïa la ki briew na ka kti jong nga, bad na ka kti ki kpa jong nga: sa katno tam ba U Blei jong phi lei lei un ym lah pyllait ïa phi na ka kti jong nga?’ ”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki shakri jong u ki la nang kren shibun shuh pyrshah ïa U Trai U Blei, bad pyrshah ïa u shakri jong U, u Hesekaïah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la thoh ruh ki shithi ïa ka ban kren pynkheiñ burom ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, bad ïa ka ban kren pyrshah ïa U, u da ong, “Kumba kita ki blei jong ki jaid bynriew jong ki ri, ki bym shym pyllait noh ïa la ki briew na ka kti jong nga, kumta U Blei u Hesekaïah un ym pyllait ïa ki briew jong u na ka kti jong nga.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki la pyrta da ka ktien bajam ha ka ktien Jiw ha ki briew ka Jerusalem kiba la don halor ka kynroh, ban pynsheptieng ïa ki, bad ban pynkhuslai ïa ki; khnang ba ki lah ban jop ïa ka nongbah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ki la kren shaphang U Blei ka Jerusalem, kumba shaphang ki blei jong ki kynja bynriew jong ka pyrthei, kiba long ki jingtrei jong ki kti ki briew.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u syiem, bad u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa u khun u Amos, ki la duwai namar kane, bad ki la lynñiar sha bneng.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te U Trai u la phah ïa u angel, uba la pynïap ïa ki riewshlur badonbor baroh, bad ïa ki nongïalam bad ki kaptan, ha ka jaka shong dara u syiem ka Assyria. Kumta, u la leit phai sha la ka ri da ka khmat balehrain. Te haba u la poi hapoh ka ïing u blei jong u, kita kiba la mih na ka kpoh jong u hi ki la pynïap ïa u hangta da ka waitlam.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumne U Trai u la pyllait im ïa u Hesekaïah bad ïa kiba shong ha Jerusalem na ka kti u Sennakherib u syiem ka Assyria, bad na ka kti jong kiwei pat baroh, bad U la ïalam ïa ki ha kiei kiei baroh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te shibun ki la wallam ki jingai ha U Trai sha Jerusalem, bad kiei kiei bakordor sha u Hesekaïah u syiem ka Judah: kumta, ba la kyntiew ïa u ha khmat ki jaid bynriew baroh naduh kata.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, u Hesekaïah u la pang ïa ka ban ïap: te u la duwai ha U Trai; te U la kren ha u, bad U la ai ïa u ka dak.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, u Hesekaïah um shym la ai pat katba kum ka jingmyntoi ba la leh ha u; namar ïa ka dohnud jong u la pynmeng: namar kata, ka jingbitar ka la long halor jong u, bad halor ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> La kumta ruh, u Hesekaïah u la pynrit ïa lade namar ka jingsarong ka dohnud jong u, ma u bad kiba shong ha Jerusalem ruh, kumta, ka jingbitar U Trai kam shym la wan halor jong ki ha ki sngi u Hesekaïah.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la don ka spah bad ka burom shibun eh: bad u la pynkhreh ïa u ki ïing jingkynshew ïa ka rupa, bad ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ki mawkordor, bad ïa ki masla, bad ïa ki stieh, bad ïa ki jaid baroh ki khiew ki pliang babha;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ki ïing jingkynshew ruh ïa ka jingmih u Kew bad ka Waiñ bad ka umphniang; bad ki sem ïa har rukom ki mrad, bad ki kynhun langbrot ha ki jingker.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nalor kita, u la pynkhreh ïa u ki nongbah, bad ki jingdon da ki kynhun blang bad kynhun masi shibun namar U Blei u la ai ïa u shibun eh ka spah.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Une ujuh hi u Hesekaïah u la set noh ruh ïa ka umpohliew ba haneng jong ki um ka Gihon, bad u la wallam ïa ki beit na shaphang sepngi ka nongbah u Dabid. Te u Hesekaïah u la man bha ha ki kam jong u baroh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, ha ka kam ki nongkit-'tien syiem jong ki rangbah Babilon, kiba la phah ha u ban kylli shaphang ka jingphylla ba la leh ha ka ri, U Blei u la iehnoh ïa u, ban tynjuh ïa u, ba un tip baroh kaba la don ha ka dohnud jong u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te kiba sah na ki kam u Hesekaïah, bad ki jingleh babha jong u, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Jingithuhpaw u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa u khun u Amos, ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Judah bad Israel.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Hesekaïah u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka thiep ki jingtep ki khun u Dabid: te baroh ki Judah bad kiba shong ha Jerusalem ki la lehburom ïa u ha ka jingïap jong u. Bad u Manasseh u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Manasseh u la long khat-ar snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar, bad u la synshar sanphew san snem ha Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, katba kum ki jingijli ki nongmane bleithaw, ïa kiba U Trai u la beh noh ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar u la tei pat ïa ki jaka bajrong ïa kiba u Hesekaïah u kpa jong u, u la pynduh noh; bad u la pynïeng ki duwan ïa ki Baal, bad u la thaw ïa ki Asherah, bad u la mane ïa u paid ka bneng baroh, bad u la shakri ïa ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la tei ki duwan ha ka ïing U Trai, ïa kaba U Trai u la ong, “Ha Jerusalem ka kyrteng jong nga kan long ha la ka rta.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la tei ki duwan ïa baroh u paid ka bneng ha baroh ar ki phyllaw ka ïing U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la pynïaid ruh ïa la ki khun lyngba ka ding ha ka them u khun u Hinnom; bad u la leh byrtong, bad u la leh myntor, bad u leh shong blei, bad u la leit sha kita kiba shong ksuid, bad sha ki nongleh byrtong: u la leh bymman shibun ha khmat U Trai, ban pynkhih bitar ïa U.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la buh ïa ka dur ba la mut jong kata ka bleithaw, ïa kaba u la thaw, ha ka ïing U Blei, ïa kaba U Blei u la ong ha u Dabid bad ha u Solomon u khun jong u, “Ha kane ka ïing, bad ha Jerusalem, ïa kaba nga la jied na ki jaid Israel baroh, ngan buh ïa ka kyrteng jong nga ha la ka rta:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> lymne ngan ym pynkynriah shuh ïa ka kjat u Israel na ka ri kaba nga la buh ïa ki kpa jong phi; lada tang ba kin sumar ban leh baroh ïa kaba nga la hukum ha ki, ïa ka hukum bad ki aiñ bad ïa ki rukom baroh keiñ da ka kti u Moses.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Manasseh u la pynbakla ïa ki Judah bad ïa kiba shong ha Jerusalem, kumta ba ki la kham leh bymman ban ïa kaba la leh ki jaid bynriew, ïa kiba U Trai u la pynjot ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Manasseh, bad ha ki briew jong u: hynrei, kim shym la suidñiew.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, U Trai u la wallam halor jong ki ïa ki kaptan u paidïapom u syiem ka Assyria, kiba la kem ïa u Manasseh ha ki kynjri nar, bad kiba la khum ïa u da ki 'saikhum, bad ki la leit lam ïa u sha Babilon.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba u la long ha ka jingshitom, u la kyrpad ïa U Trai U Blei jong u, bad u la pynrit ïa lade shibun ha khmat U Blei ki kpa jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la duwai ha U; bad u la kyrpad ïa U, bad U la sngew ïa ka jingkyrpad jong u, bad U la wallam ïa u pat sha Jerusalem ka hima jong u. Te u Manasseh u la tip ba U Trai u long U Blei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te hadien kane, u la tei ka kynroh ba kham habar sha ka nongbah u Dabid, shaphang sepngi jong ka Gihon, ha ka them, haduh ka jingbsut ka khyrdop dohkha keiñ; bad u la ker kut baroh sawdong ïa ka Ophel, bad u la pynjrong ïa ka shibun eh: bad u la buh ki kaptan bashlur ha ki nongbah ba ker kynroh baroh ka Judah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u la pynduh noh ïa ki blei nongwei, bad ïa kata ka dur bleithaw na ka ïing U Trai, bad ïa ki duwan baroh ba u la lah tei ha u lum ka ïing U Trai, bad ha Jerusalem, bad u la bred noh ïa ki na ka nongbah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u la tei ïa ka duwan U Trai, bad u la ainguh halor kata da ki jingkñia ka jingainguh bapynïasuk bad ki jingainguh, bad u la hukum ïa ki Judah ban shakri ïa U Trai U Blei ki Israel.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> La kumta ruh, ki paidbah ki shu dang kñia ha ki jaka bajrong, hynrei, tang ha U Trai U Blei jong ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kiba sah na ki kam u Manasseh, bad ka jingduwai jong u ha U Blei jong u, bad ki ktien jong ki nongïohi kiba la kren ha u ha ka kyrteng U Trai U Blei ki Israel, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki hapdeng Ki Kam Jong Ki Syiem Israel.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka jingduwai jong u ruh, bad kumno ba u la kyrpad ïa U Blei, bad ka pop jong u baroh bad ka jingpalat jong u, bad ki jaka ha kiba u la tei ki jaka bajrong, bad u la buh ïa ki Asherah bad ki dur ba la mut, mynshuwa ba u la pynrit ïa lade: ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Jingïathuhkhana u Hosai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, u Manasseh u la thiah bad la ki kpa, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka ïing jong u hi; bad u Amon u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U Amon u la long arphew ar snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar ar snem ha Jerusalem.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, kumba la leh u Manasseh u kpa jong u: te u Amon u la kñia ha ki dur ba la mut baroh ïa kiba u Manasseh u kpa jong u, u la thaw, bad u la shakri ïa ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te um shym la pynrit ïa lade ha khmat U Trai, kumba u Manasseh u kpa jong u, u la pynrit ïa lade; hynrei, une u Amon u la nang leh nang leh palat.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki shakri jong u ki la ïashet pyrshah ïa u, bad ki la pynïap ïa u ha ka ïing jong u hi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, ki briew jong ka ri ki la pynïap baroh ïa kita kiba la ïashet pyrshah ïa u syiem Amon; bad ki briew jong ka ri ki la thung syiem ïa u Josaïah u khun jong u ha ka jaka jong u."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Josaïah u la phra snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar, bad u la synshar ha Jerusalem laiphew wei snem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la leh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat U Trai, bad u la ïaid ha ki lynti u Dabid u kpa jong u, bad um shym la phai bakla sha kamon ne sha kadiang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar ha ka baphra snem ka jingsynshar jong u, haba u dang kham khynnah, u la sdang ban wad ïa U Blei u Dabid u kpa jong u: bad ha ka snem ka bakhat-ar u la sdang ban pynkhuid ïa ka Judah bad Jerusalem na ki jaka bajrong, bad na ki Asherah, bad ki durblei ba la mut, bad ki durblei ba la saiñ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki la pynkyllon ïa ki duwan jong ki Baal ha khmat jong u, bad u la khet noh ïa ki durblei ka sngi, kiba la long hajrong halor jong ki; bad ïa ki Asherah, bad ki durblei ba la mut, bad ki durblei ba la saiñ, u la pynkheiñ lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa ki, bad u la pynlwet bin bin ïa ki, bad u la khalah ïa ka halor ki jingtep jong kita kiba la kñia ha ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la thang ïa ki shyieng jong ki lyngdoh halor ki duwan jong ki, bad u la pynkhuid ïa ka Judah bad ïa ka Jerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad kumta, u la leh ha ki shnong Manasseh bad Ephraim bad Simeon, haduh Naphtali keiñ, ha ki jingjot jong ki kylleng sawdong.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la pynkyllon ïa ki duwan, bad u la shoh lwet ïa ki Asherah bad ki durblei ba la mut, bad u khet noh ïa ki durblei ka sngi ha ka ri Israel baroh, bad u la leit phai sha Jerusalem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ha ka bakhatphra snem ka jingsynshar jong u, haba u la lah pynkhuid ïa ka ri, bad ïa ka ïing, u la phah ïa u Shaphan u khun u Asaliah, bad ïa u Maaseïah u nongsynshar ka shnong, bad u Joah u khun u Joahas u nongthoh rekord, ban shna pat ïa ka ïing U Trai U Blei jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki la wan ha u Hilkiah u rangbah lyngdoh, bad ki la aiti ïa u sbai uba la wallam ha ka ïing U Blei, uba ki Lebi, ki nongap jingkhang, ki la lum na ka kti ki Manasseh bad ki Ephraim, bad na ita i bynta basah baroh na Israel, bad na ki Judah bad Benjamin baroh, bad na kiba shong ha Jerusalem baroh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki la ai noh ïa u ha ka kti ki nongtrei kiba khmih ïa ka ïing U Trai; bad kita ki nongtrei kiba la trei ha ka ïing U Trai ki la ai ïa u ban pynbha bad ban shna pat ïa ka ïing:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ha ki misteri bad ki nongtei keiñ ki la ai ïa u, ban thied u maw ba la shtah, bad ki dieng shankhung, bad ban thaw ki bim ïa ki ïing kiba ki syiem ka Judah ki la pynduh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kita ki briew ki la leh hok ïa ka kam: bad ki nongkhmih ïa ki, ki la long u Jahath bad u Obadaïah, ki Lebi, na ki khun u Merari; bad u Sekharaïah bad u Meshullam, na ki khun ki Kohath, ban pyntrei ïa ka, bad kiwei pat na ki Lebi, baroh kat kiba nang ha ki jingtem rwai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki long ruh halor ki nongkit jingkit, bad ki la pyntrei ïa baroh kat kiba trei ïa kano kano ka kam: bad na ki Lebi la don ki nongthoh, bad ki nongkam, bad ki nongap khyrdop.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad haba ki la pynmih ïa u sbai ba la wallam ha ïing U Trai, u Hilkiah u lyngdoh u la shem ïa Ka Kitab Ka Hukum U Trai ba la ai da u Moses.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Hilkiah u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u Shaphan u nongthoh, “Nga la shem ïa Ka Kitab Ka Hukum ha ka ïing U Trai.” Bad u Hilkiah u la aiti ïa kata Ka Kitab ha u Shaphan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Shaphan u la leit rah ïa kata Ka Kitab ha u syiem, bad u la wallam ktien pat ruh ha u syiem, u da ong, “Ïa baroh ba la aiti ha ki shakri jong me, ki leh ïa kata.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki la shim lut noh ïa uta u sbai ba la shem ha ka ïing U Trai, bad ki la ai ha ka kti ki nongkhmih, bad ha ka kti ki nongtrei.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Shaphan u nongthoh u la ïathuh ha u syiem, u da ong, “U Hilkiah u lyngdoh u la ai ïa nga Ka Kitab.” Bad u Shaphan u la pule na ka ha khmat u syiem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba u syiem u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien kata Ka Hukum, u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u syiem u la hukum ïa u Hilkiah, bad u Ahikam u khun u Shaphan, bad u Abdon u khun u Mikah, bad u Shaphan u nongthoh, bad u Asaïah u shakri u syiem, u da ong,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Khie leit ïakylli na U Trai na ka bynta jong nga, bad na ka bynta kita kiba sah ha Israel bad ha Judah, shaphang ki ktien kane Ka Kitab ïa kaba la shem: namar ka bakhraw ka jingbitar U Trai ïa kaba la theh halor jong ngi, namar ki kpa jong ngi kim shym la sumar ïa ka ktien U Trai, ban leh katba kum kata baroh ba la thoh ha kane Ka Kitab.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, u Hilkiah, bad kita ïa kiba u syiem u la hukum, ki la leit sha ka Huldah ka nongïathuhlypa, ka tnga u Shallum u khun u Tokhath, u khun u Hasrah, u nongsumar ki jaiñ; (ka te ka la shong ha Jerusalem ha Mishneh;) bad ki la kren ha ka kumta.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ka la ïathuh ha ki, “Kumne u ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel: To ïathuh ha uta u briew uba la phah ïa phi ha nga,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, Ha khmih, ngan wallam ïa ka basniew ha kane ka jaka, bad halor kiba shong ha ka, ïa ki jingtim baroh keiñ ïa kiba la thoh ha kata Ka Kitab kaba ki la pule ha khmat u syiem ka Judah:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> namar ki la lyndet ïa nga, bad ki la thang ka jingiwbih ha kiwei pat ki blei, ba kin pynkhih bitar ïa nga da ki kam ki kti jong ki baroh; namar kata, ïa ka jingbitar jong nga la theh noh halor kane ka jaka, bad yn ym pynlip ïa ka.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, ha u syiem ka Judah, uba la phah ïa phi ban ïakylli na U Trai, kumne phin ong ha u, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai U Blei ki Israel: Shaphang kita ki ktien kiba me la ïohsngew,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> namar ba ka dohnud jong me ka long kaba jem, bad me la pynrit ïa lade ha khmat U Blei, haba me la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien jong U pyrshah ïa kane ka jaka, bad pyrshah ïa ki nongshong jong ka, bad me la pynrit ïa lade ha khmat jong nga, bad me la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad me la ïam ha khmat jong nga; nga ruh nga la ïohsngew ïa me,’ ” ong U Trai.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Ha khmih, ngan ïalum ïa me sha ki kpa jong me, bad yn ïalum ïa me sha ka jingtep jong me ha kaba suk, lymne ki khmat jong me kin ym ïohi ïa kata ka basniew baroh katba ngan wallam halor kane ka jaka, bad halor ki nongshong jong ka.” Te ki la wallam ktien pat sha u syiem.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la phah bad u la ïalum lang ïa ki tymmen basan ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem baroh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u syiem u la leit kiew sha ka ïing U Trai, bad ki rangbah Judah baroh bad kiba shong ha Jerusalem, bad ki lyngdoh, bad ki Lebi, bad u paidbah baroh, ki bakhraw bad ki barit: bad u la pule ha ki shkor jong ki ïa ki ktien Ka Kitab Ka Jutang baroh kaba la shem ha ka ïing U Trai.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u syiem u la ïeng ha ka jaka jong u, bad u la pynlong ka jutang ha khmat U Trai, ban bud ïa U Trai, bad ban sumar ïa ki hukum jong u, bad ïa ki jingphla jong u, bad ki aiñ jong u, da la ka dohnud baroh, bad da la ka mynsiem baroh, ban leh ïa ki ktien ka jutang ïa kiba la thoh ha kane Ka Kitab.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u la pynleh ïa kiba la shem ha Jerusalem bad ha Benjamin baroh ba kin ïeng skhem ha ka. Te kita kiba shong ha Jerusalem ki la leh katba kum ka jutang U Blei, U Blei ki kpa jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Josaïah u la pynduh noh ïa ki jingijli baroh na ki ri baroh kiba la dei ha ki khun Israel, bad u la pynleh ïa kita baroh kiba la shem ha Israel ban shakri, ban shakri ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki keiñ. Baroh ki sngi jong u kim shym la kynriah na kaba bud ïa U Trai U Blei ki kpa jong ki."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Josaïah u la rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha U Trai ha Jerusalem: bad ki la pynïap ïa Ka Jinglait ha ka bakhatsaw sngi u bnai u banyngkong.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la buh ïa ki lyngdoh ha la ki kam jong ki, bad u la pynshlur ïa ki, ïa ka jingshakri ka ïing U Trai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki Lebi kiba hikai ïa ki Israel baroh, kiba la long ki bakhuid ha U Trai, “To buh ïa ka synduk ka jutang bakhuid ha ka ïing kaba u Solomon u khun u Dabid u syiem ki Israel u la tei; kan ym don jingkit shuh ha ki tyrpeng jong phi: mynta to shakri ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi, bad ïa ki Israel ki briew jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad to pynkhreh ïa lade da ki ïing ki kpa jong phi ha ki jingkylliang jong phi, katba kum ka jingthoh u Dabid u syiem ki Israel, bad katba kum ka jingthoh u Solomon u khun jong u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad to ïeng ha ka jaka bakhuid katba kum ki bynta ki ïing ki kpa jong ki para jong phi ki khun u paidbah, bad to kan long ïa uwei uwei ka bynta na ka ïing ki kpa ki Lebi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad to pynïap ïa Ka Jinglait, bad to pynkyntang ïa lade, bad to pynkhreh ïa ki para jong phi, ban leh kat kum ka ktien U Trai da ka kti u Moses.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Josaïah u la ai ha ki khun u paidbah, na ka kynhun, ïa ki khun langbrot bad ki khun blang, kine baroh ïa ka jingainguh Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ha kita baroh keiñ kat kiba don, ha ka jingkheiñ laiphew hajar, bad lai hajar ki masi dab: kine kiba long na ki mar u syiem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki rangbah jong u ki la ai kum ka jingainguh sngewbha ha u paidbah, ha ki lyngdoh, bad ha ki Lebi. U Hilkiah bad u Sekharaïah bad u Jehiel, ki nongsynshar ka ïing U Blei, ki la ai ha ki lyngdoh ban long ki jingainguh Ka Jinglait, ar hajar hynriewspah ki langbrot, bad laispah ki masi dab.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Konaniah ruh, bad u Shemaïah bad u Nethanil, ki para jong u, bad u Hashabiah bad u Jeiel bad u Josabad, ki rangbah ki Lebi, ki la ai ha ki Lebi ban long ki jingainguh Ka Jinglait, san hajar ki langbrot, bad sanspah ki masi dab.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, la pynkhreh ïa ka kam, bad ki lyngdoh ki la ïeng ha la ka jaka, bad ki Lebi ha la ki ïing kylliang katba kum ka hukum u syiem.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la pynïap ïa Ka Jinglait, bad ki lyngdoh ki la synreit ïa ka snam, kaba ki la pdiang na ka kti jong ki, bad ki Lebi ki la puid snieh ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la pynkynriah ïa ki jingainguh thang, ba kin ïoh ai noh ïa ki, katba kum ki bynta ki ïing ki kpa ki khun u paidbah, ban ainguh ha U Trai, kumba la thoh ha Ka Kitab u Moses. Bad kumba ki la leh bad kita ki masi dab.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki la syang ïa Ka Jinglait da ka ding, katba kum ka rukom: bad ïa ki jingainguh bakhuid ki la shet ha ki khiew, bad ki dek, bad ki pliang, bad ki la leit rah kloi ha ki khun u paidbah baroh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te hadien kata, ki la pynkhreh ïa lade bad ïa ki lyngdoh; namar ki lyngdoh ki khun u Aaron ki ïadonkam eh ha ka ban ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang bad ka khleiñ haduh ba la miet: namar kata, ki Lebi ki la pynkhreh ïa lade, bad ïa ki lyngdoh ki khun u Aaron.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki nongrwai ki khun u Asaph ki la don ha la ki jaka, katba kum ka hukum u Dabid, bad u Asaph, bad u Heman, bad u Jeduthun u nongïohi u syiem; bad ki nongap khyrdop ki la don ha ka khyrdop baroh: bad kim donkam ban leit noh na la ka jingshakri, namar ki para jong ki, ki Lebi ki la pynkhreh ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, ïa ka jingshakri U Trai baroh la pynkhreh ha kajuh ka sngi, ban rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, bad ban ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang halor ka duwan U Trai, katba kum ka hukum u syiem Josaïah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki khun Israel kiba la don hangta ki la rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha kata ka sngi, bad ïa Ka Jingkhawai U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat, hynñiew sngi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ym shym la don Ka Niam Ka Jinglait kat kata ba la rakhe ha Israel naduh ki sngi u Samuel u nongïathuhlypa; lymne ym don na ki syiem ki Israel kiba la rakhe kum kata Ka Niam Ka Jinglait kumba u Josaïah u la rakhe, bad ki lyngdoh, bad ki Lebi, bad ki Judah bad ki Israel baroh kat kiba la don, bad ki nong Jerusalem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ïa kane Ka Niam Ka Jinglait la rakhe ha ka bakhatphra snem ka jingsynshar u Josaïah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hadien kane baroh, haba u Josaïah u la lah khreh ïa ka templ, u Nekho u syiem ka Ijipt u la leit kiew ban ïaleh thma ïa ka Karkhemish hajan ka Ïuphratis: u Josaïah u la leit mih ban ïaleh ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, u la phah ki nonglam-ktien ha u, u da ong, “Nga donkam aïu bad me, ko syiem ka Judah? ngam shym wan ïaleh bad me ha kane ka sngi, hynrei, ïa kata ka ïing ïa kaba nga don ka thma; bad U Blei u la hukum ïa nga ban pynkloi: to iehnoh, wat ïashang bad U Blei, uba long bad nga, ba un ym pynjot ïa me.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> La kumta ruh, u Josaïah um treh ban phai la ka khmat na u, hynrei, u la pynkylla dur ïa lade, ba un ïoh ïaleh bad u, bad um shym sngap ïa ki ktien u Nekho, na ka shyntur U Blei, bad u la wan ban ïaleh ha ka them Megiddo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki nongsiat khnam ki la siat sha u Josaïah; bad u syiem u la ong ha la ki shakri, “To shim noh ïa nga; naba nga la mong jur.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumta, ki shakri jong u ki la rah noh ïa u na ka kali, bad ki la buh ha ka ba-ar ka kali kaba u la don, bad ki la wallam ïa u ha Jerusalem, bad u la ïap, bad ki la tep ha ka jingtep ki kpa jong u. Te ki Judah baroh bad ki Jerusalem ki la ïambriew ïa u Josaïah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Jeremaïah u la rwai sngewsynei ïa u Josaïah, bad baroh ki nongrwai shynrang bad kynthei ki la kren shaphang u Josaïah ha ki jingrwai sngewsynei jong ki, haduh kane ka sngi; bad ki la pynlong rukom ïa ki ha Israel: te ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ki Jingrwai Sngewsynei.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te kiba sah na ki kam u Josaïah, bad ki jingleh babha jong u, katba kum kata kaba la thoh ha Ka Hukum U Trai,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ki kam jong u, ki banyngkong bad ki bakhatduh, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Judah bad Israel."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki briew jong ka ri ki la shim ïa u Jehoahas u khun u Josaïah, bad ki la thung syiem ïa u ha ka jaka u kpa jong u ha Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Jehoahas u la long arphew lai snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar lai bnai ha Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u syiem ka Ijipt u la pynduh syiem ïa u ha Jerusalem, bad u la shaiñ kuna ïa ka ri, shispah talent rupa bad shi talent ksiar.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u syiem ka Ijipt u la thung syiem ïa u Eliakim u para jong u halor ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem, bad u la pynkylla “Jehoïakim” ïa ka kyrteng jong u. Bad u Nekho u la shim ïa u Jehoahas, u para jong u bad u la leit lam ïa u sha Ijipt.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Jehoïakim u la long arphew san snem ka rta, haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khatwei snem ha Jerusalem: bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon u la wan kiew ban ïaleh ïa u, bad u la khum ïa u ha ki 'saikhum, ban leit lam ïa u sha Babilon.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Nebukhadnessar u la kit noh ruh kiba na ki khiew ki pliang ka ïing U Trai sha Babilon, bad u la buh ïa ki ha ka templ jong u ha Babilon.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kita kiba sah na ki kam u Jehoïakim, bad ki jingijli jong u kiba u la leh, bad kata ïa kaba la shem ha u, ha khmih, la thoh ïa ki ha Ka Kitab Ki Syiem Israel bad Judah: bad u Jehoïakhin u khun jong u, u la synshar ha ka jaka jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Jehoïakhin u la long phra snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar lai bnai bad shiphew sngi ha Jerusalem: bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ynda ha kawei ka snem, u syiem Nebukhadnessar u la phah, bad u la wallam ïa u sha Babilon, lem bad ki khiew ki pliang kiba itynnad ka ïing U Trai, bad u la pynlong syiem ïa u Sedekaïah u para jong u halor ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Sedekaïah u la long arphew wei snem ka rta haba u la sdang ban synshar; bad u la synshar khatwei snem ha Jerusalem:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad u la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong u; um shym pynrit ïa lade ha khmat u Jeremaïah u nongïathuhlypa uba kren na ka shyntur U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la ïaleh pyrshah ruh ïa u syiem Nebukhadnessar, uba la lah pynsmai ïa u da U Blei: hynrei, u la pyneh ïa la ka ryndang, bad u la pynkhlaiñ ïa la ka dohnud ïa ka ban ym phai sha U Trai U Blei ki Israel.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nalor kata ruh ki rangbah baroh jong ki lyngdoh, bad u paidbah, ki la leh palat shibun eh ha kaba bud ïa ki jingijli baroh jong ki nongmane bleithaw; bad ki la pyntngit ïa ka ïing U Trai ïa kaba u la pynkyntang ha Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Trai U Blei ki kpa jong ki, u la phah sha ki da ki nonglam-ktien jong u, u da khie dang step bad u phah; namar u la sngewsynei ïa la ki briew, bad ïa la ka jaka shong.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, ki la rkhiebeiñ ïa ki nonglam-ktien jong U Blei, bad ki la ñiewbeiñ ïa ki ktien jong u, bad ki la pyrthuhbeiñ ïa ki nongïathuhlypa jong u, haduh ba ka jingbitar U Trai ka la mih pyrshah ïa ki briew jong u, katba ym don jingshna shuh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar kata, u la wallam halor jong ki ïa u syiem ki Khaldi, uba la pynïap ïa ki samla jong ki da ka waitlam ha ka ïing ka jaka kyntang jong ki, bad um shym isynei ïa u samla lane ïa ka samla, ïa u tymmen lane uba la 'dor ryngkdung: u la ai noh ïa ki baroh ha ka kti jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ïa ki khiew ki pliang baroh ka ïing U Blei, kiba khraw bad kiba rit, bad ïa ki jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai, bad ki jingkynshew u syiem, bad ki jong ki rangbah jong u; ïa kine baroh u la leit lam sha Babilon.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki la thang ïa ka ïing U Blei, bad ki la pynkyllon ïa ka kynroh ka Jerusalem, bad ki la thang da ka ding ïa ki ïingpaki jong ka baroh, bad ki la pynjot ïa ki khiew ki pliang ba-itynnad jong ka baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ïa kita kiba la lait na ka waitlam, u la leit lam noh sha Babilon; bad ki la long ki shakri ïa u bad ïa ki khun jong u haduh ka jingsynshar ki Persha:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ïa ka ban pyndep ïa ka ktien U Trai da ka shyntur u Jeremaïah u nongïathuhlypa, haduh ba ka ri ka la ïoh bha ïa la ki Sabbaton: naba katba ka la sah kynjah ka la rakhe ïa ka Sabbaton keiñ, ïa ka ban pyndep hynñiewphew snem.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ha ka snem ka banyngkong u Seiros u syiem ka Persha, ba yn pyndep ïa ka ktien U Trai da ka shyntur u Jeremaïah, U Trai u la pynkhih ïa ka mynsiem u Seiros u syiem ka Persha, katba u la pynbna ha ka hima jong u baroh, bad u la thoh ruh ïa kata, u da ong,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Kumne u ong u Seiros u syiem ka Persha, ‘Ïa ki hima baroh jong ka khyndew U Trai U Blei ka bneng U la ai ha nga: bad U la hukum ïa nga ban tei ka ïing ïa U ha Jerusalem, kaba ha Judah. Kino kino kiba don hapdeng jong phi na ki briew jong U baroh, to U Trai U Blei jong u, Un long ryngkat bad u, bad to un leit kiew.’ ”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;